Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.24,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Dean, and this is The MongoDB Podcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:05.72,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Today we're going to be talking about a game I made called "osu!".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:09.15,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Welcome to The MongoDB Podcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:12.15,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And as ever, thanks for joining us for another episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.43,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,My name is Shane McAllister,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:17.56,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and if it's not too late, happy new year to all our listeners.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:21.12,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And we're very much looking forward to SUPERB 2023,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:24.12,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and some exciting episodes to bring your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:27.68,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So as ever, please remember to hit that subscribe button...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:29.99,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,on whatever podcast pot from you use,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:31.76,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,so you don't miss a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:35.83,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,On this week's episode, we dive into the area of gaming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:39.09,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and more particularly, beat matching and rhythm games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:43.01,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And I'm delighted to be joined by Dean Herbert, founder of osu!.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:46.50,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,osu! is a hugely popular online rhythm game.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:51.44,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,It's open source and uses the Realm .NET SDK from MongoDB.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:56.80,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And in this episode, we learn more about its inception, why Dean built it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:01.94,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and how it's grown hugely in the many years since Dean single handily built it himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.13,0:01:05.55,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and how he's turned his hobby into his day job,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.70,0:01:08.83,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and built a huge and loyal community following.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:10.32,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Let's jump right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:14.24,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,On the show, today, we are joined by Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:18.32,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Dean, please introduce yourself to the audience here in the MongoDB Podcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:20.37,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Tell us who you are and what do you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:23.87,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yep, hi, I'm Dean. I made a game called osu!.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:29.81,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Been working on it since 2007. So it's been kind of my life for the last 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:32.67,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Started off as a bit of a hobby thing, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.67,0:01:38.43,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I got into it because I was always interested in the rhythm game, and such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:41.47,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,In my childhood, I grew up in Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:46.24,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and we had arcades, which occasionally got these rhythm games in.
Comment: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:46.24,English,,0,0,0,,arcade 商场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:50.99,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And I was always into music and gaming, so that combination really struck something with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:53.41,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,But we didn't have that many arcades,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:58.09,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and quite often they would shut down, all these games would just disappear, out of the blue.
Comment: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:01.09,English,,0,0,0,,out of the blue 出人意料的                没过多久它们就会关闭，所有这些游戏就会突然消失。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:00.05,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So when the Internet came around and,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:03.53,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,these people were making online simulators of these rhythm games,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:08.03,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and suddenly I had access to play the games whenever I wanted on my PC.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:10.39,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So that's kind of how this is born out of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:12.68,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So take us back to the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:16.43,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Ask there's a Japanese meaning behind the name? And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:19.44,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,for our audience who are quite wide and varied,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:22.39,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,who mightn't understand rhythm and beat matching games,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:25.53,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,can you explain a little bit about where they originated from,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:27.29,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and what's involved in playing those?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:28.25,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.75,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So there's a lot of different styles of rhythm games,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.32,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,but osu! is based on,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:36.43,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,it's actually based on a game which was published by an Nintendo on the Nintendo DS,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:39.43,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and that game is called '{\i1}Osu! Tatakae! Ouendan{\i0}'.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:42.67,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and it was kind of a story driven game where,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.93,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,you would play through this journey with cheerleaders,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.81,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,they are actually male cheerleaders called the ouendan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:52.88,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And the word 'osu!' in that is kind of part of their chant which,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:55.88,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,which they're like trying to encourage people that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:59.59,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,have these stories in life where they've, you know, hit at the rock bottom.
Comment: 0,0:02:59.59,0:02:59.59,English,,0,0,0,,hit the rock bottom 跌入低谷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:02.88,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And you have to play along to the game in time with the music,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:06.83,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,tapping on the Nintendo DS screen to get them into a better state of mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.11,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and quite often save the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:10.65,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So It was born out of that. I played that game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:14.48,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And obviously, because it was published to a mobile system,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:17.51,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,you are limited to play the levels that were included in the game, and,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:21.08,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I immediately wanted to add my own songs into the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.25,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,you know, to create new levels for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:24.88,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So that's, that's how osu! was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:29.79,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Okay, so it's, it's 15 years ago since this inception.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:33.00,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,What size is it now? What sizes the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:35.52,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and what's your day to day role in the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:40.36,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Maybe for the first five or even more years, it was just me working on the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:43.69,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Started off as a hobby, and I eventually I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:47.04,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I originally was employed full time as a .NET developer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:50.83,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I was working on migrating some J2EE systems across the .NET. So,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:55.00,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,yeah, I had a good experience, with a good amount of experience with .NET.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.36,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yeah, over the years, it was originally just me and I kind of,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.80,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,moved from the game being a side project of being full time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:06.15,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,As people started to show more interest in the game and actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:08.68,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,financially contribute to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:11.56,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,That's fascinating, because I think in my own past,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:15.13,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,I've met a lot of developers who are frustrated game developers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:17.57,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,you know, so they go down the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:21.05,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,exactly what you're describing, Dean, which is, you know, following their passion,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:22.83,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,following something that they're interested in. But,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:26.37,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,it's, it's really, really hard to turn that into the day job,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.20,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,but you've managed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:30.44,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess, um, a certain degree of luck there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:33.95,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And just I had a huge amount of passion towards the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:37.00,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,so I was spending every waking hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:42.41,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Oftentimes I was sleeping like 3 hours a day for like, years at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:47.07,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Back when I was of a younger age, I constantly went on this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:50.16,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,so people saw the amount of change I was putting into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:52.12,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and the amount I was listening to users' feedback,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:54.39,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I guess, and giving them exactly what they asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:58.11,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yet, in the early days, I made some very rapid development progress,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:00.57,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,maybe at the detriment of code quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:04.19,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,But, yeah, over the years, we have increased the size of the teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:07.19,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I think there's about eight of us full time working on the game now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:11.04,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,various elements of the game, the client and the infrastructure behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:15.93,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And then we also have a huge amount of community contributions, so,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:18.93,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,basically volunteers that keep the user content,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:22.97,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,the curation systems of the game, running the moderation of the online community.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:26.17,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And so you're based in Japan. Where are the rest of the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:29.49,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Are they in Japan as well too? Are they spread globally?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:32.36,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yes, so we do have a few devs over in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.71,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,but most of the team is working remotely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.01,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,We ve always, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:40.71,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,basically promoted people up from these volunteer roles into kind of full time roles,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:43.53,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and they've just been working from wherever they are in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:46.27,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So we have a few in America, some in Australia,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:49.27,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,some in East Asia as well, different areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:52.52,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Wow, that's excellent. So obviously there,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:57.32,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,you mentioned the inception was from the game that you saw, an Nintendo game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:00.60,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,There's obviously other kind of rhythm matching, beat matching games out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.47,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,What sets osu! apart from those?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:07.12,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I guess the main thing is that we've always been very community driven,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:09.79,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,focused on user content. So from day one,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:12.72,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,the game kind of shipped with an editor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.39,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,where you could create these levels in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.25,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,The game never came with levels included.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:20.95,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,It's always up to the user to create that content.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:23.95,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yeah. And the other thing is, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:26.51,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I guess I've always tried to run the game very differently...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:29.11,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,to how the industry is progressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:33.55,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I'm not a huge fan of the, um, the monetization of gaming these days, so,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:37.81,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,so I've always done things the way I would want them to be done if I was a user of the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:40.23,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,has never been about getting profit from the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.37,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Okay, so you're taking it from that perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:47.55,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So I think, you know, certainly it brings us to the question of revenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:50.45,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And I know, and I've been browsing the osu! site,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.93,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,you've got an amazing swag store. I love the plushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.04,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And obviously there's and silary revenue there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:07:00.93,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,But how does osu! supported? How is your team of eight developers supported?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:03.44,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yeah, so we do have the merchandise side of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.27,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,but that doesn't really um that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:08.81,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,That only covers basically the tournament prizes side of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:12.64,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,These days, most of our revenue comes from people just donating to the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:15.57,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,We have this system called Supporter Tags,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:21.40,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,which is basically the ability to buy or donate, contribute for x months or x years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.07,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And you get a few in-game perks,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:26.11,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,things like more customization for your profile,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:30.56,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and just a few features inside the game that make it more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:32.77,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,easy to access certain features of the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:37.25,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,ability to operate more content than normally uses. Just a few perks like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:40.00,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I've always tried to keep the perks that you get ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:42.36,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,limited to things which actually cost us more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:44.36,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So there's actually a tangible mapping...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.01,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,of the many people paying to what they get in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.72,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,That's very interesting. And I suppose, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:53.21,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,we are used to the larger gaming sphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:57.35,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,where that is not always the most altruistic intentions there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:08:02.29,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,it's profit and large as and building bigger and bigger games and bigger developer teams...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:06.99,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,at bigger cost, etc. as well too. And I will get later on, hopefully, into the community,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:10.05,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,because that is super impressive, what you are doing your community.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:13.09,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,But just again, to fill in the background, you mentioned that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:17.51,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,you know, you launched it, it didn't come with any beatmaps there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.72,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,You had to create them yourself. How does that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:21.93,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,What is a beatmap? How are they made?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:25.57,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And how many have people created over the time that you've run osu!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:27.40,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yes, so that's the other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:31.76,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,When I first made the game, there were other simulators on the PC platform but,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:37.13,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,they didn't really come with the tools that let you jump straight into to creating the level. So,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:42.52,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So I basically from the main menu of the game, you can go into the editor and then use...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:45.52,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Drag any MP3 you want to create a level for,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:51.65,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and set up the timing, so you tap in time to the to the song to get the BPM set up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:55.23,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and then you can just start placing objects on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:57.49,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So we have three different kinds of objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:09:01.55,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,There's like Standard Hits, and then Hold Hits, which run over duration,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:04.04,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and then Spin as, which is a kind of gimmick,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.75,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,where you have to spin as fast as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.68,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So it gives you a lot of flexibility over what you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.91,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,how you want to create the level for the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:14.16,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,The other aspect is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:17.85,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,when you place these objects, you can give them special sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:23.16,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So you can actually create, like almost a drum rhythm over the original song,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.57,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,which gives it a new character.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:29.63,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And this is one of the main reasons I actually was very interested in this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:32.09,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,more so than other rhythm games, is that Nintendo,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:35.84,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,or INIS, which is the original publisher, they created these...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:38.31,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,all my soundscapes on top of the original songs,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.23,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and they just stuck in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:43.64,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Every time I heard a song on the radio, I could hear these.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.15,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I wanted to add these rhythms on top of the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:50.31,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Okay, so when you're uploading an MP3, is that any MP3,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:54.16,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,or is there a copyright reason, issues, etc. As well, too, I would imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:58.16,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So it's it's all local when you'd actually drag the MP3 in,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.92,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,so you can, in theory, had anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.64,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And, oh, I see, so you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:07.04,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,so you're creating the beatmap on top of a popular piece of music,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.93,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,but yes, your local piece of music.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:12.19,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,But we do allow that to be upload to the service.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:15.69,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So I guess it was a very great area for a long period of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:17.33,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,where people were uploading this content.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:19.80,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,We obviously take it down whenever we get requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.51,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,But the other thing that was really good is once we...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:27.12,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,over the last five or six years, and we actually started turning in a good profit,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:30.97,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I've contributed to all that profit back to licensing the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:32.72,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So we've gone back retroactively,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:36.59,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and all the most popular levels that have been uploaded to the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:41.16,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,We've reached out to the artists, and we've got something like 4000 license tracks now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.93,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,which I think is the most of any rhythm game out there. So we've,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:48.27,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So we've tried our best to bring that back around, into the legal realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:51.47,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,I love this story. This is great. And overall,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:54.39,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,how many tracks have been uploaded to osu!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:58.72,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's, there's something over 2 million, I think, levels have been created.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:02.11,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And then of that, we have, like a process which...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:04.63,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,ensures that some of the levels are very high quality,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:07.64,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and they get what we call the ranked status, which, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:09.16,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,gives them leaderboards. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:10.89,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,if you have the special features,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:13.52,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and I think we have something like 50000 of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.81,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Wow. So speaking of numbers in that scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.07,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,what size is the osu! community?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:21.39,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,How many players do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:24.05,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,What sort of countries are they in? How often do they play?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.09,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Sure, yes. So we um,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:29.08,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,we've got something like 30 million registered users now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:31.72,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,The concurrent user base is something...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:35.57,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,in the range of 20 to 40 thousand during the peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:39.32,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Over the last few years, we had huge influx of users during COVID,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:44.07,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,that got us up to something like 48000 concurrent users at peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:49.68,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,We see people playing, like every month, about two to three million people come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:54.63,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So that's the ongoing user base, I guess, is around two, two mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:57.08,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Wow. This is amazing, Dean. I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:12:00.43,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,obviously I've spoken with you before, and we've interacted over a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.75,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,but I did not know this stats with this large.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:05.27,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,That is, they are sort of numbers that most...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:08.24,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,game companies and businesses alone would kill for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:10.37,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,That is incredible that you built this from...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.57,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,the inception yourself and then threw into the small team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:17.67,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And more important, the style and the nature with which you've been building this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:21.64,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And I know you said earlier, community is really big to osu!,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:25.01,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and you have, you've contests and tournaments and live streams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.63,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Tell us a little bit about those.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:30.25,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yeah. So all our tournaments are basically community run.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:33.39,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,We do have an official one, which is called the osu! World Cup,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:38.73,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Very topical for the moment, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:41.61,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,That is, like, it's financially supported by us,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.76,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,but it's still run heavily by the community.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:46.64,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And yeah, we have various contests going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:51.87,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,so things like fan art contests and composition contests for songs to be used in the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:53.95,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and also for the levels, obviously,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:56.51,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,as we do a lot of ongoing things like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:59.59,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,just to invigorate the community, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:02.77,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Yeah. So you have, as you said, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:06.12,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,you run into 30 million registered, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.89,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,tens of thousands, kind of concurrently, etc. as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:11.99,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,We talk a little bit about the tech stack in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:14.25,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,but where is your most popular country?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.37,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,What's, you know, going back to the beatmaps,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:19.01,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,is there a very popular style of beatmap?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.03,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Or do they go in and out of vogue?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:25.77,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yes. So, uh, the top countries, I guess, is the US and Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:29.69,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So we have had a bit of drop off in financial support on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:32.89,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,one of those two over the last year or so, went due to world events.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.64,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,But yeah, over the years, that has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.31,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So we used to have a huge Asian following. But,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:41.89,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,but it seems like certain countries come in and go out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:46.35,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and the style of music we see, or beat maps, it really does vary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.88,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,We have basically every genre you could think of,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:52.67,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,but the most popular levels in the game are the ones which...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:55.67,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,seem to give higher score than they should.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:14:00.00,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,so people are willing to get to, yeah, to get the highest score in levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:01.92,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So there's one which is 30s long,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:06.19,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,that people are constantly retrying to get the highest score,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:08.09,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and that's, that's one of our most popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:10.96,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So they're doing that to basically level up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:13.96,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And it's pretty much you have to keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:17.41,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yes, yeah, it's all about increasing a statistics.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:20.88,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And when I looked at... you have a great table on the website...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.76,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,for rankings and country rankings and player ranking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:26.03,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And, you know, when you go into the users,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:30.61,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,I see users play counts of into the hundreds of thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:33.69,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So is that cumulatively over the years?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:34.75,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,It is, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:35.96,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Do they do anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:40.11,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,It would see if you had things in a hundred hundreds of thousands, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:43.60,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,One of the most impressive things to me is there's actually people that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:45.35,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,stream this game full time these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:47.23,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and they're making a living of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:49.76,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,they're supporting their own production teams of a game that I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:51.40,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and that just kind of blows my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:54.67,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,In some cases, I think they're actually making more than the game itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:56.88,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,That's an interesting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:02.32,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,That is, yeah, I mean, we see the rise of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:05.86,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,certainly over the last number of years, and again, particularly during COVID when,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:08.59,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,people are at home and, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:09.92,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,you've multi screens as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:13.05,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,so I think a lot of people stream in the background while they're,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:14.16,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Um, Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:17.27,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,That's incredible. That's a great community. Yeah, most definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:19.85,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,This is, you know, sounds really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:23.68,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,If I want to get started with osu!, what do I do? Where do I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:25.75,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,How do I get playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:31.16,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yep. So you can grab the game off our website: osu.ppy.sh
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:33.01,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Or if you want to try out the new version,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:37.41,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,which we've currently been basically rewriting the game from the ground up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:40.53,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and that's on GitHub right now. That's the open source, part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.89,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Go to @ppy on GitHub, I'm sure you'll find it pretty easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:47.73,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And yet, all the account registration, everything's done from the game itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.37,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:52.73,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Great, and I see that, I loved. I went into the rules section.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:56.39,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Your community rules are very fair, very equitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:16:01.33,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,But the first one is that you have one account, and one account only for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:05.96,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Can you explain to me a little bit about that decision why you went down that and,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:07.83,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and purely to stop gamification?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:11.53,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Basically, it's to ensure the integrity of the leaderboards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:14.41,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,If people were allowed to create as many accounts as they want,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:18.52,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,you would see people like showing up at like, rank one, rank two, rank three.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:20.75,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So that's the main reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.64,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,It's kind of just stuck that way over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:25.03,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,It's one of the harder rules to enforce, as you can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:27.68,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,I can imagine. Yes, how do you please that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:31.71,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,We have various metrics are similar to, I guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:34.71,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,what advertising companies do to track people online.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:36.24,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,We do our best, but also,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:38.69,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,we generally don't enforce that rule unless we need to,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:42.57,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,unless we see people actually be abusing the system to a greater extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:45.20,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So like my thinking is, is always that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:49.59,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,if people aren't causing detrimental experience to other users,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.67,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,if they're not affecting the general user experience, then I don't really,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:54.88,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,put too much effort into tracking them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:57.80,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So we know where to go, we know where to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:59.68,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Obviously, if you're only getting it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:04.21,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,you have a lot of ground to make up with all of the other players and everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:06.31,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,But, the other thing is that it's a very casual game,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:09.21,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,so you can just jump in, play once and, you know, never come back, or,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:11.13,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,you know, play it very casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.61,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,It's not one of the games where you have to be competitive...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:16.51,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,or keep up with the ongoing systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:19.81,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,OK, so you can dip in and out,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:23.95,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,as time permits, and, you know, as...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:27.01,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yeah, you don't have to put several hundred thousand hours into the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:28.40,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,or whatever people are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.95,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Very good, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:32.35,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So talk to me a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:35.35,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Let's get deeper into the technology behind, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:36.09,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:40.47,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Like, with that sort of numbers, with that large amount of registrations,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:42.20,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,that amount of current users,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:46.43,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,I'm really keen to understand a little bit more about how you built it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:49.16,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and what are the core technologies behind it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:52.29,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yeah, so, um, it's, it's actually an interesting one,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:55.23,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,because I did a talk recently on the infrastructure,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:59.87,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and I got a lot of feedback from people being very impressed with how,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:03.57,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,um, how lane our team is on our infrastructure for the size of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:06.44,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And that's something I've always aimed for is, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:08.57,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,to keep things as simple as possible, because,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:12.08,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I've been basically single handling, running the infrastructure for the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.01,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,even to this date.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:15.60,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I do have one other person helping me with, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:17.96,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,some migration we are doing to Kubernetes these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:20.00,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,kind of containerize everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:24.68,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,But we our infrastructure these days, it's changed over the years, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:26.51,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,as we've had to scale up to more users.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:30.92,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,But we are using, um, DigitalOcean as our main host for cloud hosting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:36.44,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,We run something like 150 different Droplets doing different stuff on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:39.21,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And then we also use S3 for storage
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:43.51,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and OVH for some of the higher bandwidth distribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:48.55,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I wonder things is we don't rely on Steam or any other distribution platforms,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:53.33,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,so we kind of have to bear that ourselves, all the updating infrastructure,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:56.48,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,everything is kind of ridden from the ground up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:19:00.76,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,That's one of the things that really interests me, so I enjoy doing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:04.04,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,keeping it all completely independent of these other systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:08.87,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Sure. And in the time that you've been doing it, then, Dean, what has changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:13.77,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Obviously, you know, you mentioned DigitalOcean and S3, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:18.53,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,But if you've been building this initially, starting yourself 15 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:21.73,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,you've seen a huge amount of changes in the tech landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:24.20,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And then how, you know, where did you start?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:27.65,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,How did you manage the changes over time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:29.77,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,the migrations that you needed to do, etc.?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:31.11,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yep. So, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:34.60,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I did originally start was just running on my home server, basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:39.69,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,back in the late 2000, 2008, 2009,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:41.49,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and then gradually scaled up from there,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:45.39,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,so went to share hosting, then dedicated service, then more dedicated service.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:50.29,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Then at some point got a bit annoyed at switching between hosting platforms,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:54.11,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,um, because I had to basically rent out servers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:59.13,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,It was very hard to get a good level of remote support from these hosting companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:03.31,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So when DigitalOcean came around, it was very enticing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:06.47,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,you know, virtualizing this and making it a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:11.25,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,easier to migrate between different servers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:14.47,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And also they had a very good support,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:16.57,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,to a level that I had never experienced before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:19.91,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,We've, we... our database is MySQL,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:22.01,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and we've had to scale that up over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:24.16,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,We used to have just a single database,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:27.92,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,but these days it's something like 5 different service running in a small cluster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:31.48,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And, yeah, just constant scaling, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:34.19,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Excellent. Excellent. And why we're on that subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:40.57,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Let's talk a little bit about why, uh, I came to meet you a year or two ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:45.20,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,you're migrating across to using Realm from MongoDB.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:48.73,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Tell us about that process. Why did you start that? How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:52.67,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,How long did it take? And what's been the benefits of doing that for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:57.68,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yep. So I'll just mention that, uh, this is going onto the clients side of things now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:00.68,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So we, we've been using .NET, .NET framework originally,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:05.36,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and in 2017, I basically decided it was time to rewrite the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:07.75,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and to go for completely open sources part of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:11.23,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Um, it's always been one of my goals to keep as transparent as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:13.93,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,so switching to open source was like a no brainer at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:16.51,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So we switched to .NET Core,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:20.49,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,um, we were using SQLite,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:24.09,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,along with, um, Entity Framework Core in the early days,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:29.79,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and that worked quite well, but we were using it in a very haphazard way,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:34.16,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,because Entity Framework was kind of made more for websites,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:36.83,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,where everything is has a very same threading model.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:38.69,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,You've got a request coming in and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:41.03,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,you're doing various things across that request.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:43.36,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And that's the lifetime over a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:44.92,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,with a game. That's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:47.51,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,It's running for, you know, potentially hours on end,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:51.13,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and we have all these threads doing different things accessing the same data.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:55.15,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So, EF while it worked for us, it was a very haphazard set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:58.25,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and as we tried to migrate from EF2 to EF3,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.51,0:22:02.48,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,we just hit all these issues where they had enforced all these new rules with threading,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:04.45,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and we couldn't make it work for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.81,0:22:08.68,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So I wanted to fix out threading model,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:11.24,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,our data access model, and Realm had this um.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:14.48,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,It was really enticing to me. It has asset compliance,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.48,0:22:17.75,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and it really, Realm is very stringent in...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:21.75,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,how it allows you to do threading, which I saw as a benefit,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:24.80,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,even though we would have to put in some initial effort to get that working.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:26.71,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,It meant that we could really streamline,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:30.95,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,streamline our data access and be forced to do things in a in a good way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:33.20,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,It's quite opinionated, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.48,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yes, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:37.91,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Yes, in a good way, though, as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:38.64,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.36,0:22:42.37,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So you commenced that, I think, probably when we first spoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.37,0:22:47.00,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,it was towards the end of 2020, the beginning of 2021.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:49.80,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And it was completed a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:55.25,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So, and I would imagine it's not a task you undertook light handedly,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.25,0:23:00.41,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,given the scale, you know, this rewrite of the game that you were doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:01.84,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Yeah, so, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.47,0:23:05.56,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,one of the things with osu! is it's a very data driven game,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.56,0:23:07.68,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,because most of the content is user created.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.68,0:23:13.12,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,We have basically this huge, local, client side database,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:16.39,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and that's one of the main reasons I put so much thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.39,0:23:20.75,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and yet wait into the decision to get this right and to switch to Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.15,0:23:24.75,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I think I had tried it probably three times over from scratch...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:27.21,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,before I actually figured out how we could make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.60,0:23:31.03,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And it was a huge undertaking, but it turned out okay in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:33.60,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Luckily.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.75,0:23:36.45,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,I'm very happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:41.12,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And I know that the Realm team is, particularly on the .NET SDK team,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:45.93,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Nikolan and the others, we had some to and forward back conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.93,0:23:49.04,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And indeed, you helped us a lot by things that you discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.44,0:23:54.27,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Usually, what we find building RSDKs is that we're, I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.27,0:23:57.77,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,like most developers, nearly too close to the bone sometimes to figure out...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.15,0:24:00.11,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,how this is going to get used in the real world,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:04.91,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and that it falls and in issues somebody else developing on it might have.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.91,0:24:10.32,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So I very much appreciated the interaction that you had with our development team in that, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.57,0:24:14.40,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And because that helped us a lot. And I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.81,0:24:19.67,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,the developers I know in Realm love to hear of it being used out in...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.67,0:24:21.37,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,the real world and for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.61,0:24:24.03,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And that's been very beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.03,0:24:27.21,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So you're very happy ultimately with how that went.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.97,0:24:30.84,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,For sure. And, um, yeah, we've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.84,0:24:35.84,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Currently it's pushed out to desktop platforms, so Windows, Linux and macOS.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.84,0:24:38.21,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and Realm is working great across all those platforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.21,0:24:43.01,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,We also have it on Android and iOS, but it's kind of in a beta state.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.15,0:24:44.75,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,We're planning on pushing that out further.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.75,0:24:50.40,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,But yet, Realm has allowed us to basically push out all these platforms with no issues at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.69,0:24:52.43,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's been a dream to work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.53,0:24:56.44,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Even with SQLite, getting the native dependencies right across all these platforms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.44,0:24:58.35,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,it's kind of on you as a developer,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.67,0:25:01.87,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,while Realm kind of has everything kind of in place to make that work.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.75,0:25:06.14,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,That's great to hear. I'm going to cut this snippet of the podcast out,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.14,0:25:08.58,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and I'm going to send it on to the engineering team.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.06,0:25:12.09,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,They would be delighted to hear that first hand feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.59,0:25:17.15,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,You touched on it earlier in so far as osu! in this change...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.15,0:25:21.56,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,that you started in 2017 with the rewrite, you went open source.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.73,0:25:22.99,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Tell us the reasoning behind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.45,0:25:26.43,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So I've always been about transparency in the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.55,0:25:31.63,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,with how we develop it, and, you know, trying to give back as much to the community,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.63,0:25:35.47,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,but also give back to the development community.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.57,0:25:40.07,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,A lot of players are also we have a very,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.21,0:25:43.70,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I guess, a relatively young audience in the community,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.70,0:25:46.74,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and a lot of the people that are playing the game are also, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.89,0:25:49.25,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,growing up and getting into game development themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.58,0:25:54.31,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So I saw that there was a potential to give back to these players as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.31,0:25:58.71,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,get more involvement, not only on the side of content creation,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.71,0:26:00.98,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,but having people contribute to the game itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.98,0:26:04.59,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And yet, over the years, like even before we went open source,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.70,0:26:06.79,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I had a lot of people ask me if they can help with the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.79,0:26:09.00,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and we did bring in quite a few people,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.00,0:26:12.58,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,but there was always this barrier of having a closed source code base,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.87,0:26:15.13,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,where it wasn't very easy to share things upwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.57,0:26:19.99,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Yeah. And, and look, obviously, I mean, that's the main benefit of open source indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.99,0:26:22.85,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,You know, MongoDB origins come from there as well too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.25,0:26:25.55,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,How do you manage to...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.73,0:26:29.59,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,handle those contributions and kind of the PRs that you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.59,0:26:34.93,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,You know, I notice from the website, e.g. that it seems that updates are going out weekly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.28,0:26:38.89,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,You have a huge change log there. There's lots of people helping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.89,0:26:43.89,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,How is that managed from your small team as well too, Dean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.89,0:26:48.13,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Uh. With a lot of stress on the side of some developers,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.55,0:26:53.21,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,it's a huge flood of incoming poor requests and issues we get.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.31,0:26:57.21,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And this is before we've even gotten live with this open source version.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.21,0:26:59.32,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Like it's still very much in a testing state,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.77,0:27:02.91,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and we've hold back pushing it out to the full user base until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.91,0:27:06.62,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,because we know that we're just going to get flooded with even more incoming support requests...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.62,0:27:08.89,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,as we get more users on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.31,0:27:12.53,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So the new version has something in the range of hundreds of...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.71,0:27:15.83,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,thousands of users that have ever opened it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.01,0:27:19.98,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Whereas the actual game is, you know, several magnitudes higher than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.57,0:27:23.87,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yet, I can't really say much about how we manage it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.89,0:27:28.73,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Apart from that, it's still an ongoing point of conflict and point of concern...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.88,0:27:30.55,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,how to actually keep up with this,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.68,0:27:35.63,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,this flow of open source contributions and discussions, everything else that comes with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.94,0:27:38.45,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,I suppose that's one of the things from...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.45,0:27:41.18,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,when you go down this route of open source with the community,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.63,0:27:43.37,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,it's a good complaint, almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.37,0:27:46.65,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,You know, you have a lot of PRs, you've got a lot of people raising issues,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.65,0:27:48.79,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,you've got a lot of people helping you out to fix things.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.04,0:27:51.16,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,But there is that management side of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.23,0:27:55.24,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,But from my eyes, from what I've seen, you're doing a superb job.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.24,0:27:57.55,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And to keep them, you know, keep it alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.55,0:28:03.53,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So, um, that seems kind of a huge amount of work to manage that level of enhancements.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.53,0:28:06.53,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And I think that's great. So this is Project Lazer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.27,0:28:08.11,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yes, great, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.65,0:28:11.27,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So, it's been in gestation for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.27,0:28:16.20,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,When will you push it out fully to the wider community?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.20,0:28:19.25,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think we, we started on this in something like 2017,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.25,0:28:23.91,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and I think we are finally at the point where maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.91,0:28:27.45,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,we get this pushed out completely this year, next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.87,0:28:29.21,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Everything is pretty much in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.21,0:28:31.88,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,But it's more about the user acceptance side of things now,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.11,0:28:33.94,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,making sure that all the features that people,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.15,0:28:38.32,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,because we build up a huge amount of features in the games...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.32,0:28:41.64,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,over the years that people have come to expect to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.19,0:28:46.40,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And the way I developed the game originally, it was, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.40,0:28:50.36,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,just about getting the maximum throughput in features,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.36,0:28:52.35,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,not worrying about the codes quality too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.35,0:28:53.88,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,These days, we're doing the exact opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.88,0:28:57.23,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,We're making sure that the game is maintainable into the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.34,0:29:01.50,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,even if I was to stop working on it, or, you know, disappear and someone had to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.98,0:29:06.11,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yeah, trying to keep everything completely documented and...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.11,0:29:09.20,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,in a way that someone would be, like, very excited to take over the project,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.20,0:29:13.08,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,rather than look at this code base and be like, "oh my God, what have I end up with?"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.40,0:29:18.07,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And is there anything currently kind of hampering your growth,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.07,0:29:21.52,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,or your scale, or you happy with where everything is at the moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.52,0:29:25.62,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Or is there, you know, something that's kind of a an ongoing frustration,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.62,0:29:29.09,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,be it technical, be it reach of your community?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.42,0:29:32.12,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I don't think so. No. The main, the main concern is,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.12,0:29:34.11,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,just getting this new version out to the users,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.20,0:29:37.42,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and, you know, figuring out what needs to be done,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.51,0:29:41.22,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,what's left to be done to satisfy the vast majority.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.76,0:29:46.76,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And I guess the hardest thing there is managing the community,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.76,0:29:50.48,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,managing the feedback we get from users in this day and age,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.48,0:29:54.77,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,where the vocal minority is often very, very vocal about...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.77,0:29:56.86,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,things that are missing or things that are done wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.10,0:29:59.82,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,putting this into perspective, the larger part of the community,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.82,0:30:01.57,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,which is very happy with how things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.35,0:30:06.68,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and also just supporting the different hardware that people are running on and,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.68,0:30:08.94,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and getting good performance out of, you know, devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.94,0:30:12.06,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,People are potentially playing this game on PCs from the,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.70,0:30:15.63,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,like, ten years ago, 15 years ago, and they expected to run well.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.63,0:30:18.82,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So, you know, re-engineering with the latest libraries and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.82,0:30:21.37,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,but also getting that backwards compatibility is a huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.43,0:30:23.77,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,It is tough to manage those multiple platforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.77,0:30:26.96,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,As you say, you're on Windows and Linux and macOS, and,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.39,0:30:30.90,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,in beta, well, a mobile in iOS and Android, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.42,0:30:34.49,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,But very much in kind of beta environment for there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.79,0:30:36.78,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,I think, as you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.78,0:30:40.08,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,there's a saying that the squeaky wheel gets the most oil,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.08,0:30:43.21,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and I think that's what you're trying to get out there with your community.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.21,0:30:46.62,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,There's that people who will always be the most vocal,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.62,0:30:49.53,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,but yeah, they could be very much in the minority.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.53,0:30:53.90,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And as you said, the satisfied users, and again, you can attest to...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.97,0:30:57.00,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,you know, your hundreds of thousands of users, maybe on...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.00,0:31:01.57,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and lazer, versus the much more larger group who are very happy and content with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.57,0:31:06.02,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,are the ones that you're not necessarily eliciting the feedback from other than...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.02,0:31:07.48,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,they're happy to keep playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.69,0:31:09.77,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yeah, but the other thing to remember is that,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.77,0:31:12.84,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,this feedback usually comes from a good place, like these,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.84,0:31:15.24,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,these people are very vocal because they care about the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.24,0:31:19.52,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and they care about getting from the game exactly what they and potentially others expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.52,0:31:23.75,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,So we do definitely trail our hardest to listen to every single piece of feedback,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.75,0:31:28.07,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And you know, I try my best to reply every email I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.07,0:31:32.67,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,It's quite a huge time sink for me actually keeping up with the community.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.67,0:31:36.68,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,But I feel it's important, even if that takes away a bit from development time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.86,0:31:41.45,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And I suppose, obviously lazer, that's the biggest next step,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.74,0:31:43.47,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,getting it out to the rest of the community.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.23,0:31:46.85,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Is there an agenda beyond that, Dean?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.85,0:31:50.66,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Is there, once that stone, we're going to do X, Y, or Z?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.66,0:31:52.71,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,or even something that you could maybe tell us about, or,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.71,0:31:55.16,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,or does that get that out and take a long holiday?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.63,0:31:59.88,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Well it, I mean, I would love to, one of the things I'd really like to do is,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.88,0:32:02.69,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,uh, work on a different project, but, like, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.69,0:32:06.53,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,try something new, or potentially work for someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.53,0:32:07.82,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and just, you know, take a step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.82,0:32:09.19,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,But I don't think that's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.40,0:32:12.50,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,At this rate, we have this huge backlog of features, which,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.85,0:32:16.02,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,currently we're trying to get, you know, feature parody with the old version.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.02,0:32:19.84,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,But after that, there's so much users' requests that I just don't see an end in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.03,0:32:21.25,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,It's, it's a bit scary,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.50,0:32:23.35,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Don't see the end, it's a bit scary,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.35,0:32:26.05,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,but it's a challenge that obviously you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.49,0:32:29.15,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,given your 15 years with this so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.41,0:32:29.73,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.03,0:32:35.75,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,given the fact that you've turned something that was a hobby and an interest into a business,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.75,0:32:40.18,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and actually employed other people to do that, and built this massive global community,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.25,0:32:42.67,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,I don't think anybody wants you to step away from this, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.67,0:32:46.15,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and I think they're obviously looking to build more and more and,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.30,0:32:47.49,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and broaden this,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.88,0:32:50.89,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,For sure, and like I wouldn't want to wish on anyone else what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.89,0:32:55.29,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I think it takes like, a certain degree of insanity to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.29,0:32:57.24,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,to take on this role.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.49,0:33:00.51,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,But yet, at the same time, one thing I will say is that,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.23,0:33:04.44,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,like, no matter what happens in the future, I'm very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.44,0:33:07.24,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I'm very content with everything we've achieved to the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.24,0:33:10.28,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And I think it's important to, like, take these things day by day,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.28,0:33:15.22,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and just being like so many people have enjoyed this game over the last 15 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.56,0:33:18.63,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,it's like we could destroy everything today,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.63,0:33:21.13,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,and I would still be content with the fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.13,0:33:24.25,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,we've been given so much enjoyment back over the last decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.25,0:33:27.95,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I have to heap nothing but praise on you for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.13,0:33:29.72,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,from everything that you've talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.72,0:33:35.86,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And obviously that enjoyment is a reward in itself for you having built this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.21,0:33:38.87,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And the facts, I in my view, anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.87,0:33:43.98,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,the fact that you haven't tried to overtly grow this beyond its means,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.98,0:33:47.56,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,or overtly monetize it or put barriers in the way of play.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.93,0:33:52.31,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And that by kind of the supporters' tags that you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.31,0:33:56.52,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,you're saying, well, look, we do need some revenue here to keep this going,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.52,0:33:59.18,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,but we know what we need and we know how to go about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.18,0:34:01.98,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And I think that there's something incredibly altruistic about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.98,0:34:04.69,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,as well as open source, as well as how you manage that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.69,0:34:08.37,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So I think you've done a stunning effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.37,0:34:12.96,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and I very much look forward to the continued growth of osu! going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.96,0:34:16.89,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Is there anything else you'd like to share with the podcast audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.89,0:34:19.72,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And people out there, as I alluded to earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.72,0:34:24.16,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,there's a lot of developers out there who would love to take their hobby,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.16,0:34:26.55,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,their interests, into their day job.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.93,0:34:30.74,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And you obviously have done this. You've walked the walk, talk the talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.15,0:34:34.75,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Any advice for those sort of developers that might be teetering on that edge?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.75,0:34:38.68,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Particularly because with COVID, people have been working from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.68,0:34:42.95,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,They now realize that you don't need an office, forsay, to go to,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.95,0:34:46.52,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,You don't need to turn up in a particular place for a particular supplement of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.56,0:34:50.94,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So the opportunities, I think, are presenting themselves to developers to,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.24,0:34:54.47,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,to take on their own projects and side projects,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.47,0:34:55.83,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and maybe seek and they run with.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.83,0:35:00.65,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think, um, the way I've always saying it is, all my side projects.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.65,0:35:03.25,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Everything I've worked on has been something that I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.25,0:35:07.09,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,both been interested in and something that I've wanted to exert myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.09,0:35:09.63,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Whether that's improving and existing service...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.88,0:35:11.57,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,that doesn't quite do what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.73,0:35:14.68,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I always build for myself and then push it out to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.68,0:35:16.90,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,And if that catches on, then it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.90,0:35:21.09,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,But I'm, I'm not really developing things with, you know, marketing,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.09,0:35:23.92,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,or whether it's financially viable in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.92,0:35:28.09,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,I think that's important thing is to set off just trying to build an amazing product.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.33,0:35:32.10,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,There's so many examples of that in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.10,0:35:36.52,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,particularly in the tech space of developers scratching an itch, something they wanted to fix,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.52,0:35:40.28,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,that all of a sudden pivoted and snowballed and grew into something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.28,0:35:42.60,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,But I think in your case, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.60,0:35:47.60,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,I'm really impressed with what you've built at osu! and how you've gone about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.60,0:35:49.53,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And this has been a fascinating conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.53,0:35:53.97,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So for the listeners, before we finish, where again,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.97,0:35:56.37,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,just remind us where we can go to play it,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.63,0:36:01.67,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,or the GitHub repo, to go and become part of the community and contribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.87,0:36:06.19,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Ah, yep. So you can go to, osu.ppy.sh to grab the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.33,0:36:10.12,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,or you can go to GitHub. @ppy is our organization, and everything's listed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.20,0:36:11.79,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Excellent. This has been great.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.79,0:36:14.09,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,I do appreciate your time in joining us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.17,0:36:17.84,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And as you said earlier, you don't view this as work.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.92,0:36:20.90,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,I can attest to that, because you're in Japan. I'm in Ireland.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.90,0:36:24.50,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,We've got a nine hour time difference. It's super late your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.88,0:36:26.99,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,You're more than happy to jump on this podcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.27,0:36:29.02,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And for that, I thank you, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.02,0:36:31.40,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So we do appreciate you join in us,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.40,0:36:35.04,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and we look forward to following the progress of osu! as it goes forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.54,0:36:37.52,English,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,Yep. Thanks, Shane, what's a great conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.54,0:36:42.33,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,As you can probably tell, I really enjoyed my conversation with Dean,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.65,0:36:47.55,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and it amazes me the level of commitment he has to osu! and to the osu! community.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.06,0:36:52.02,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,It really stands out that this is more than a job or a business for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.45,0:36:56.71,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,and that behind everything there's a sense of purpose, community and vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.34,0:37:00.94,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,I very much look forward to watching the continued success of osu!.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.24,0:37:02.85,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,If you want to try it out for yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.20,0:37:07.50,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,the links to the website and repos mentioned in the show are in the shown notes,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.84,0:37:09.46,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,so do check those out, also.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.34,0:37:13.13,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Like Dean, if you have a story of interest to our listeners,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.38,0:37:16.62,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,we're always looking for guests on The MongoDB Podcast,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.93,0:37:18.95,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,so if you feel that you can contribute,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.30,0:37:23.31,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,do get in touch with us at podcast@mongodb.com.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.63,0:37:25.25,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,And we'd very much love to hear from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.47,0:37:29.34,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,Thanks again for listening. We really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.56,0:37:31.92,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,If you did enjoy this episode, as ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.92,0:37:37.50,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,pleased to leave us a rating and even a review on whatever podcast platform you use.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.78,0:37:39.02,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,It really does help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.56,0:37:42.83,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,So for me, Shane McAllister, and the rest of the podcast team,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.46,0:37:46.82,English,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,until next time, do take care, and thanks for listening.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.24,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,你好   我是 Dean   这里是 MongoDB 播客
Comment: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:05.72,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,今天我们来聊聊我创造的一款叫 osu! 的游戏
Comment: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:09.15,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,欢迎来到 MongoDB 播客
Comment: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:12.15,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,和往常一样   感谢您加入我们新的一集专访
Comment: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.43,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我的名字叫 Shane McAllister
Comment: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:17.56,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,如果现在不算太迟的话   祝各位新年快乐哦
Comment: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:21.12,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,另外   我们非常期待今年的超级碗比赛
Comment: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:24.12,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,而且我们还会带来一些激动人心的专访
Comment: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:27.68,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,还是那句话   无论你用的是哪个播客软件
Comment: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:29.99,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,都请点击“订阅”按钮   关注我们
Comment: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:31.76,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,这样你就不会错过我们了
Comment: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:35.83,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,在这一周的专访中   我们要深入游戏领域
Comment: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:39.09,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,尤其是节奏游戏{\3c&H0000FF&}*{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:39.09,Explanation,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,*本视频不会译作“音游”“音乐游戏”而是“节奏游戏”，因为显然后者是前者的子集，前者还包括“旋律游戏”甚至“音量游戏”，比如《\N不要停！八分音符酱♪》。
Comment: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:43.01,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,今天很高兴邀请到 Dean Herbert   osu! 的创造者
Comment: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:46.50,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,osu! 是个倍受欢迎的在线节奏游戏
Comment: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:51.44,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,它是开源软件{\3c&H0000FF&}*{\r}   用到了 MongoDB 的 Realm .NET SDK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:51.44,Explanation,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,*新版的 lazer 客户端。
Comment: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:56.80,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,本期访谈中   我们要了解它的开端   为什么 Dean 创造了它
Comment: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:01.94,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,自从 Dean 单枪匹马地创造它以来   它是怎样在多年间取得巨大发展的
Comment: 0,0:01:02.13,0:01:05.55,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,以及他是怎么把这项爱好变成全职职业的
Comment: 0,0:01:05.70,0:01:08.83,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,他是怎么建立起一个庞大而忠诚的追随者社区的
Comment: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:10.32,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,让我们开始吧
Comment: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:14.24,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,今天   在这里   我们邀请到了 Dean
Comment: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:18.32,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,Dean   请你对 MongoDB 播客的观众做个自我介绍
Comment: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:20.37,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,告诉我们你是谁   你干的是什么
Comment: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:23.87,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,嗨   我是 Dean   我创造了一个叫 osu! 的游戏
Comment: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:29.81,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,自 2007 年来我就一直致力于此   所以在过去十五年间它成了我的一种生活方式
Comment: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:32.67,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我从一个爱好做起
Comment: 0,0:01:32.67,0:01:38.43,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我就无法自拔   因为我总是对节奏游戏和诸如此类的事情感兴趣
Comment: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:41.47,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我在澳大利亚长大   度过童年
Comment: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:46.24,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,那会儿我们还有开这种节奏游戏的机厅
Comment: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:50.99,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我一直喜欢音乐和游戏   所以这种组合真的打动了我
Comment: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:53.41,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但是那种机厅并不多
Comment: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:58.09,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,而且没过多久它们就会关闭   所有这些游戏都会突然消失
Comment: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:00.05,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,于是   当互联网出现时
Comment: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:03.53,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,有的人就做了这类节奏游戏的在线模拟器
Comment: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:08.03,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,突然间   我就又能在电脑上玩到它们   想玩啥就玩啥了
Comment: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:10.39,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这就是 osu! 诞生的背景
Comment: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:12.68,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,那我们就回到开头的话题
Comment: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:16.43,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,osu! 是有个日语含义对吧   另外
Comment: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:19.44,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我们的听众是相当广泛和多样的
Comment: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:22.39,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,有的听众可能并不了解什么是“节奏游戏”
Comment: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:25.53,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你能解释一下这些游戏的起源
Comment: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:27.29,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,玩这些会涉及什么
Comment: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:28.25,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,好的
Comment: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.75,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,节奏游戏有很多风格
Comment: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.32,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,而 osu! 是基于
Comment: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:36.43,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,是基于一款发布在 NDS 上的游戏
Comment: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:39.43,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,叫做《押忍！战斗！应援团》
Comment: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:42.67,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这是一款故事驱动的游戏
Comment: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.93,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,游戏中   你会和啦啦队队员一起
Comment: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.81,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这些队员都是男的   叫做“应援团”
Comment: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:52.88,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,而“osu!”{\fs36}(押忍！){\r}是他们的一个口号
Comment: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:55.88,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,他们想鼓励那些
Comment: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:59.59,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,那些经历过人生低谷的人
Comment: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:02.88,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,你得随着音乐玩这款游戏
Comment: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:06.83,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,在 NDS 屏幕上点击   让他们情绪高涨
Comment: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.11,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,最后拨云见日   屡战屡胜
Comment: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:10.65,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这就是 osu! 的起源   我玩了那款游戏
Comment: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:14.48,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但显然   因为它是面向一个小游戏机系统发布的
Comment: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:17.51,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,你只能玩到游戏自带的歌
Comment: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:21.08,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我就马上想要往里面加自己选的歌
Comment: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.25,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,相当于创建新关卡
Comment: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:24.88,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,于是 osu! 就诞生了
Comment: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:29.79,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,那么   自从你开始   已经十五年了
Comment: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:33.00,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,现在它规模有多大   它的团队有多大
Comment: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:35.52,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,以及你在团队中的日常角色是什么
Comment: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:40.36,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,在头五年   好像还多几年   是只有我在维护这个游戏的
Comment: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:43.69,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,开始是作为一个爱好   最后就（辞职开发游戏了）
Comment: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:47.04,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我原来是全职 .NET 程序员
Comment: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:50.83,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,当时我做的是把 J2EE 系统迁移到 .NET
Comment: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:55.00,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,所以我有丰富的 .NET 开发经验
Comment: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.36,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,是的   最初只由我业余搞搞
Comment: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.80,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这些年来   人们对这个游戏越来越感兴趣
Comment: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:06.15,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,然后他们真的投入金钱贡献
Comment: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:08.68,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,于是我就全职开发游戏了
Comment: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:11.56,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,很了不起   因为在我的过去
Comment: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:15.13,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我遇到过许多失意的游戏开发者
Comment: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:17.57,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,他们也走在（游戏开发之）路
Comment: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:21.05,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,就和你的描述一样    追寻他们的激情
Comment: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:22.83,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,追随他们感兴趣的东西
Comment: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:26.37,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,然而   把它作为全职工作真的很不容易
Comment: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.20,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,但你做到了
Comment: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:30.44,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯   或许我有运气成分在里面
Comment: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:33.95,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我就是对这游戏有极大的热情
Comment: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:37.00,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,于是我醒着的每一刻都投入其中
Comment: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:42.41,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,很多时候   我每天只睡三个小时   这样一干就是好几年
Comment: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:47.07,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,当我年轻的时候   我一直在做这个游戏
Comment: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:50.16,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,大家看到了   因为我的投入   这个游戏变化之大
Comment: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:52.12,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,（大家也看到）我倾听用户反馈的次数之多
Comment: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:54.39,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,然后我就满足他们要求的东西
Comment: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:58.11,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,早年间   我取得了一些非常快速的开发进展
Comment: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:00.57,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,也许代价就是代码质量很差
Comment: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:04.19,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但是   这些年里   我们扩大了团队规模
Comment: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:07.19,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,现在一共有八人在全职开发 osu! 了
Comment: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:11.04,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,包括游戏的各种元素   客户端及其背后的基础设施
Comment: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:15.93,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,而且我们还有大量的社区贡献
Comment: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:18.93,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,基本上   是志愿者在保持内容的产出
Comment: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:22.97,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,游戏的策划系统   运行在线社区的管理
Comment: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:26.17,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你居住在日本   团队中的其他人在哪里
Comment: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:29.49,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,他们也在日本么   还是说你们遍布世界各处
Comment: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:32.36,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,是的   我们确实有几个开发者在日本
Comment: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.71,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但大多数成员是远程工作的
Comment: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.01,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,其实我们一直
Comment: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:40.71,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,基本上把人们从志愿者角色提升到全职角色
Comment: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:43.53,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,他们一直在他们那里工作
Comment: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:46.27,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,所以有几个在美国   有几个在澳大利亚
Comment: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:49.27,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,还有些在东亚   反正是遍布全球
Comment: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:52.52,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,那很精彩诶   那么
Comment: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:57.32,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你提到最初这个游戏是基于一款 NDS 游戏
Comment: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:00.60,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,显然   世界上还有其他类型的节奏游戏
Comment: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.47,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,是什么使 osu! 与所有这些都与众不同
Comment: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:07.12,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我想主要是因为我们的动力大部分来自社区
Comment: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:09.79,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们致力于用户内容   所以 osu! 从第一天起
Comment: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:12.72,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,就自带一个编辑器
Comment: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.39,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,你可以在那里创建游戏关卡
Comment: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.25,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,osu! 从来不自带关卡{\3c&H0000FF&}*
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.25,Explanation,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,*原文如此，但事实上，安装好的游戏一直都会自带十余个谱面，且自带谱面会不定期更换。Dean 的意思应该是，osu! 没有“官方谱面”，哪怕是自带谱面也都是由普通玩家制作的。关于自带谱面的决定流程，请看评论区置顶。
Comment: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:20.95,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,要制作什么完全取决于用户
Comment: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:23.95,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,还有一件事情是
Comment: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:26.51,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们一直在尝试着以一种
Comment: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:29.11,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,与游戏工业有天差地别的方式来运营游戏
Comment: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:33.55,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我并不喜欢当今把游戏给货币化的方式
Comment: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:37.81,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,所以我总是以玩家想要的方式去运营
Comment: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:40.23,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,从未想过在游戏中获利
Comment: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.37,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,于是你就从那样的角度对待了
Comment: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:47.55,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,所以这当然会让我们想到收入的问题
Comment: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:50.45,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我浏览了 osu! 网站
Comment: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.93,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你们有家很棒的装饰品商店   尤其是那个抱枕{\3c&H0000FF&}*{\r}   我挺喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.93,Explanation,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,,*去年年末出的限量版抱枕，现已售罄。
Comment: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.04,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,很明显   那里有很多收入
Comment: 0,0:06:56.04,0:07:00.93,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,但是 osu! 是怎么坚持的呢   你们八个人靠什么吃饭
Comment: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:03.44,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,是的   所以我们确实有商品方面的东西
Comment: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.27,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但那点钱算是（杯水车薪）
Comment: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:08.81,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,那点收入只能涵盖比赛奖金之类的东西
Comment: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:12.64,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,现在   我们的大多数收入来自玩家的直接捐赠
Comment: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:15.57,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们有一套系统叫“支持者标签”
Comment: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:21.40,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,玩家买个几月几年的支持者标签
Comment: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.07,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们就给予他们一些游戏内的额外功能
Comment: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:26.11,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,比如   自定义个人主页
Comment: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:30.56,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,还有一些游戏内部的
Comment: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:32.77,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,更便利的功能
Comment: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:37.25,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,与一般玩家相比能支配的东西更多   就像这样的几个功能
Comment: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:40.00,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我一直把这些特权放在
Comment: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:42.36,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,花费我们更多精力的地方
Comment: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:44.36,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,于是这之间有了实在的关系
Comment: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.01,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,即   你出钱   就有相应回报
Comment: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.72,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,挺有趣的   另外
Comment: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:53.21,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我想我们已经习惯了更大的游戏领域
Comment: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:57.35,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,但那些游戏的赚钱心可能更强
Comment: 0,0:07:57.35,0:08:02.29,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,它的利润很大   但游戏规模也会越大   开发团队也越大
Comment: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:06.99,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,成本等等也越大   接着我们来谈谈游戏社区
Comment: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:10.05,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你运营的社区实在让人印象深刻
Comment: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:13.09,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,但是我们还得补充下背景   比如你刚才提到
Comment: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:17.51,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你创立 osu! 时   并没有现成的谱面
Comment: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.72,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你只能自己做   这是怎么回事
Comment: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:21.93,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,什么是“谱面”   谱面是怎么做的
Comment: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:25.57,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,这十多年来   玩家们一共做了多少谱面
Comment: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:27.40,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,啊   那是另外一回事了
Comment: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:31.76,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我第一次完成这个游戏时   电脑平台上已经有些这个游戏的模拟器了
Comment: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:37.13,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但它们都没有能让你能够直接创作关卡的工具
Comment: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:42.52,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,而   自 osu! 的主菜单中   你就可以进入编辑器
Comment: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:45.52,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,拖进一个你想做关卡的 MP3
Comment: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:51.65,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,对好节奏   敲鼓点来把 BPM 设置好
Comment: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:55.23,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,而后你就可以在屏幕上开始布置物件了
Comment: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:57.49,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们有三种物件
Comment: 0,0:08:57.49,0:09:01.55,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,一是圆圈   二是滑条   会持续一段时间
Comment: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:04.04,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,三是转盘   一种小把戏
Comment: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.75,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,你要以最快的速度转动
Comment: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.68,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,所以它给了你很大的灵活性
Comment: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.91,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,每首歌你都能随心所欲地制作关卡
Comment: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:14.16,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,另一方面
Comment: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:17.85,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,你在放置物件时   可以赋予它们特殊的声音
Comment: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:23.16,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,所以你实际上可以在原始歌曲上创建一个鼓点节奏
Comment: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.57,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,给予它新的特征
Comment: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:29.63,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这就是我对这个游戏感兴趣的原因之一
Comment: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:32.09,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,比起其他节奏游戏来说    任天堂的这款
Comment: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:35.84,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,应该是 INIS   他们才是原开发者   他们在原曲之上
Comment: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:38.31,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,创造了新的声音景观
Comment: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.23,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,他们存留在我的脑海中
Comment: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:43.64,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,每次我在电台里听到一首歌   我就能听到这些节奏
Comment: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.15,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我就想在原曲上加入这些节奏
Comment: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:50.31,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,所以如果你要上传一个 MP3    是任意的 MP3 都能用吗
Comment: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:54.16,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,还是说   这本身就存在版权问题   我能想象得到
Comment: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:58.16,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,你把 MP3 拖进来时    一切操作都在本地
Comment: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.92,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,所以   理论上讲   你可以做任何事情
Comment: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.64,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,那就是说   你也可以
Comment: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:07.04,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,用热门曲目来制谱
Comment: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.93,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,但它存储在本地
Comment: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:12.19,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但是我们是允许把它们上传到服务器的
Comment: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:15.69,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,所以   很长一段时间里
Comment: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:17.33,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这都是用户创作的天堂
Comment: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:19.80,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,当然   如果收到（下架）请求   我们肯定会下架
Comment: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.51,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但有件好事是
Comment: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:27.12,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,最近这五六年   我们有了可观的盈利
Comment: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:30.97,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们把这些收入都投入到音乐版权中
Comment: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:32.72,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们已经追溯到了过去那些
Comment: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:36.59,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,谱面库里最受欢迎的谱面
Comment: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:41.16,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们会联系那些艺术家   现在我们已经买下了约四千首歌的版权
Comment: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.93,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,好像是所有节奏游戏中最多的吧
Comment: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:48.27,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们已经尽力把它们带回来   能合法地使用
Comment: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:51.47,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我喜欢这个故事   挺不错的
Comment: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:54.39,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,那么    osu! 谱面库到现在一共有多少谱面呢
Comment: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:58.72,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯   超过两百万
Comment: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:02.11,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,此外   我们还有一套机制
Comment: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:04.63,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,来保证谱面的质量
Comment: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:07.64,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,叫做“上架状态”{\3c&H0000FF&}*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:07.64,Explanation,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,*“Ranked”谱面，通常译作“上架”谱面，是经过至少七名玩家（五名普通玩家和两位谱面审核成员）认可的谱面。请参见 osu! wiki 的相关章节。
Comment: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:09.16,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,上架的谱面会开放排行榜
Comment: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:10.89,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,还会有一些特殊特性
Comment: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:13.52,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,目前上架谱面大约有五万个吧
Comment: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.81,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,哇   所以说   在这个规模的谱面库上
Comment: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.07,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,osu! 社区又有多大
Comment: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:21.39,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,玩家共有多少
Comment: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:24.05,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,他们在哪些国家   他们多长时间玩一次
Comment: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.09,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,好的   那么
Comment: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:29.08,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们的注册用户大约有三千万
Comment: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:31.72,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,在高峰期   同时在线人数
Comment: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:35.57,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,在两万到四万之间
Comment: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:39.32,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,疫情这几年有大量的用户涌入
Comment: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:44.07,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,现在的同时在线人数能跑到四万八了
Comment: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:49.68,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,月活也不少   每个月大约有两到三百万人回来
Comment: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:54.63,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,因此   这就是持续的用户群   大约是两百万
Comment: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:57.08,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,这太令人惊叹了   Dean   我觉得
Comment: 0,0:11:57.21,0:12:00.43,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我以前和你谈过   我们已经互动了一段时间
Comment: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.75,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,但我不知道统计数据会有这么大
Comment: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:05.27,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,其他大多数游戏公司看到你们的数据
Comment: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:08.24,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,肯定恨不得宰了你们
Comment: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:10.37,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,不可思议的是   你只身建立起游戏
Comment: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.57,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,最后运营到一个小团队
Comment: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:17.67,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,尤其是   你构建它的风格和性质令人惊叹
Comment: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:21.64,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你之前说到   社区对 osu! 发展很重要
Comment: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:25.01,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,osu! 有比赛    锦标赛和直播
Comment: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.63,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,请谈谈这几个东西吧
Comment: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:30.25,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,那么   我们的锦标赛基本都是社区运营
Comment: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:33.39,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们也有一个官方的比赛   叫 osu! 世界杯
Comment: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:38.73,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,挺应景的   放在这里
Comment: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:41.61,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,osu! 世界杯由官方提供资金
Comment: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.76,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但还是极大程度地依靠社区运转
Comment: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:46.64,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,此外还有各种比赛
Comment: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:51.87,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,比如   同人绘画比赛   编曲比赛
Comment: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:53.95,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,当然   还有谱面的比赛
Comment: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:56.51,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们做了很多这样的持续的事情
Comment: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:59.59,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,都是为了振兴社区吧   我想
Comment: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:02.77,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,对   正如你所说
Comment: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:06.12,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你有三千万注册用户
Comment: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.89,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,数万人同时在线   等等
Comment: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:11.99,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我们待会会聊聊技术栈
Comment: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:14.25,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,但还有个问题   哪些国家的玩家最活跃
Comment: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.37,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,还有   关于谱面
Comment: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:19.01,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,谱面所用的曲子中   有没有一类最受欢迎的歌
Comment: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.03,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,还是说   它们会时而流行   时而过时
Comment: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:25.77,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯   最热门的国家   大概是美国和俄罗斯
Comment: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:29.69,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,由于疫情爆发   最近一两年
Comment: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:32.89,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们减少了对其中一个国家的资金投入{\3c&H0000FF&}*
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:32.89,Explanation,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,*似乎是指 osu! 的推广，但这与 osu! 公开的运作模式相悖。此外“world event”指的是什么也不很明确。欢迎大家讨论 peppy 想表达的是什么意思。
Comment: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.64,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但是   以前的 osu! 可不是这样
Comment: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.31,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,以前我们有大量的亚洲玩家
Comment: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:41.89,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但是这些国家的玩家时而来时而去
Comment: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:46.35,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,还有   用来制谱的音乐类型相当多样
Comment: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.88,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,你能想到什么流派   我们都有这类谱面
Comment: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:52.67,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但最受欢迎的谱面
Comment: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:55.67,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,是那种看起来会送分的谱面{\3c&H0000FF&}*
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:55.67,Explanation,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,*中文社区俗称 pp 图。
Comment: 0,0:13:55.67,0:14:00.00,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,大家都会去一次次地赌   尝试拿下榜首
Comment: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:01.92,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,有一首歌只有三十秒长{\3c&H0000FF&}*
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:06.19,Explanation,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,*举两例：Harumachi Clover  编号：842412；Make a Move  编号：765778
Comment: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:06.19,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,玩家一直在尝试得到最高分
Comment: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:08.09,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,那是我们最火的谱面之一
Comment: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:10.96,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,所以他们这样做基本上是为了升级（刷 pp）
Comment: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:13.96,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,而且你的成绩还得经得考验
Comment: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:17.41,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这都是在往上刷统计数据
Comment: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:20.88,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我看到 osu! 网站上有一张很棒的表格
Comment: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.76,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,对国家和玩家进行排名
Comment: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:26.03,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我点进用户页发现
Comment: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:30.61,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,他们都有成百上千次游玩记录
Comment: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:33.69,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,这是年复一年累计的吗
Comment: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:34.75,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,是的
Comment: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:35.96,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,它们还干别的事吗
Comment: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:40.11,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,就是说   你把时间都用在一遍遍重复这个事情上了
Comment: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:43.60,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,让我印象最深的一件事是
Comment: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:45.35,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,现在真的有玩家全天直播 osu! 了
Comment: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:47.23,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,他们就以此为生
Comment: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:49.76,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,他们正在支持我制作的游戏的制作团队
Comment: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:51.40,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这让我很震惊
Comment: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:54.67,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,在某些情况下   我认为他们实际上比游戏（官方）还赚更多
Comment: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:56.88,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,挺有趣的
Comment: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:02.32,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是说   我们看到了它的崛起
Comment: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:05.86,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,在过去的几年里   尤其是在疫情期间
Comment: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:08.59,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,人们都呆在家里
Comment: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:09.92,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你（和大家一样）手里不止一个屏幕
Comment: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:13.05,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,很多人都在家里开直播
Comment: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:14.16,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,是的
Comment: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:17.27,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,这真是不可思议   伟大的社区   的确
Comment: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:19.85,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,这个游戏听起来很有趣
Comment: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:23.68,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,如果我想要入坑 osu!   我应该做什么
Comment: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:25.75,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我要怎么玩到它
Comment: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:31.16,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,好的   你可以从我们的官网下载   osu.ppy.sh
Comment: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:33.01,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,或者   如果你想尝试新版本
Comment: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:37.41,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是我们全新重写的版本
Comment: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:40.53,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,它就在 GitHub 上   而且是开源的   部分是{\3c&H0000FF&}*
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:40.53,Explanation,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,*例如，根据官方开发博客，反作弊部分会被抽离出来，单独开发，不予开源。
Comment: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.89,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,去 GitHub 上找到 @ppy   相信你很容易找到
Comment: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:47.73,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,账户注册都在客户端内部实现了
Comment: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.37,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,就是这样
Comment: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:52.73,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,很好   我明白了   接着我们聊聊社区规则
Comment: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:56.39,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你们的社区规则是非常公平公正的
Comment: 0,0:15:56.79,0:16:01.33,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,但第一大规定就是   一人一号   终身不许开小号
Comment: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:05.96,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你能给我解释一下这个决定吗   为什么你这么做
Comment: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:07.83,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,还有为什么要纯粹地停止游戏化
Comment: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:11.53,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,基本上是为了确保排行榜的完整性
Comment: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:14.41,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,如果让玩家随心所欲地创建账号
Comment: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:18.52,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,就会出现榜一榜二榜三都是同一人的奇观
Comment: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:20.75,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这是主要原因
Comment: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.64,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,多年来   这规定就这样坚持了下来
Comment: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:25.03,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这是最难执行的规则之一   你可以想象得到
Comment: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:27.68,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我能想象   那你怎么能检测到呢
Comment: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:31.71,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们会看多重指标
Comment: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:34.71,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这些指标和广告公司的在线追踪程序类似
Comment: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:36.24,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们尽力了   但是
Comment: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:38.69,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,除非有必要   否则我们一般不会死撑这一规则
Comment: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:42.57,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,除非我们看到人们实际上在更大程度上滥用该系统
Comment: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:45.20,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我的想法一直都是
Comment: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:49.59,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,如果人们没有对其他玩家造成有害的体验
Comment: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.67,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,如果他们没有影响到全体用户的体验
Comment: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:54.88,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,那么我真的不会花太多精力去追踪他们
Comment: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:57.80,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是说   我们清楚我们的目标   和怎样实现目标
Comment: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:59.68,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,显然   如果你现在才开始玩
Comment: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:04.21,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你有很多地方需要与所有其他玩家和东西一起弥补
Comment: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:06.31,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,你别慌啊   其实它是一个非常休闲的游戏
Comment: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:09.21,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,你可以下载后只玩一次   然后弃坑
Comment: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:11.13,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,或者非常随意的玩
Comment: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.61,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这不是那种你必须保持竞争力
Comment: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:16.51,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,亦或是要跟上正在进行的系统的游戏之一
Comment: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:19.81,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,好的   也就是说   你可以自由进入或者退出
Comment: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:23.95,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,只要时间允许   想怎么玩都行
Comment: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:27.01,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,是的   你不需要在 osu! 中投入成百上千小时
Comment: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:28.40,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,也不需要和其他玩家一样氪金氪周边之类
Comment: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.95,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,非常好
Comment: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:32.35,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,让我们接着下一个话题
Comment: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:35.35,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我们来聊聊这背后的技术   Dean
Comment: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:36.09,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,好的
Comment: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:40.47,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,既然你有如此之多的注册用户
Comment: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:42.20,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,如此之多的同时在线人数
Comment: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:46.43,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我真的很想更多地了解你是如何构建它的
Comment: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:49.16,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,它背后的核心技术是什么
Comment: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:52.29,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,那将会非常有趣
Comment: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:55.23,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,因为我最近做了一个关于基础设施的讲座
Comment: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:59.87,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我就收到了听众反馈   他们对我们在
Comment: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:03.57,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,基础设施方面的表现印象相当深刻
Comment: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:06.44,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这是我一直以来的目标
Comment: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:08.57,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,就是让事情尽可能简单
Comment: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:12.08,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我基本上是孤军作战   独自运行游戏的基础设施
Comment: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.01,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,到今天也不例外
Comment: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:15.60,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我确实有一个人帮我
Comment: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:17.96,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,在这几年帮我迁移到 Kubernetes
Comment: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:20.00,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,帮我做容器化的各种工作
Comment: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:24.68,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,显然   我们的基础设施在这几年有了变化
Comment: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:26.51,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这是为了要扩大用户群
Comment: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:30.92,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,当前   我们选择 DigitalOcean 作为我们的云主机主要提供商
Comment: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:36.44,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们买了 150 个不同的 Droplet 单元   用来干不同的事情
Comment: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:39.21,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们也用 S3 做存储
Comment: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:43.51,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,和 OVHcloud 公司的一些高带宽分布系统
Comment: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:48.55,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们不依赖 Steam 或其他分发平台   这点我自己都惊讶
Comment: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:53.33,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,所以我们不得不自己承担所有基础设施的更新
Comment: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:56.48,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,一切都是从头开始的
Comment: 0,0:18:57.40,0:19:00.76,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这一点很激起我的兴趣   所以我喜欢做这事
Comment: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:04.04,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,保持这一切完全独立于这些其他系统
Comment: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:08.87,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,是的   另外   你做 osu! 的这些年   有哪些事情是改变了的   Dean
Comment: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:13.77,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,显然   你提到 DigitalOcean 和 S3 等等
Comment: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:18.53,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,但如果拉长目光   从你开始开发的十五年看
Comment: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:21.73,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你已经看到了技术领域的巨大变化
Comment: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:24.20,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,那么   你的起点在哪里
Comment: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:27.65,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你是怎么一路下来接受这些变化
Comment: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:29.77,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,完成所需要的迁移   等等
Comment: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:31.11,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,好的   那么
Comment: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:34.60,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,最初我是直接在我家里的服务器上运行的
Comment: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:39.69,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,在 00 年代末   2008 年   2009 年
Comment: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:41.49,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,从那里逐渐拓展
Comment: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:45.39,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,于是去买了共享主机   然后是专用服务   然后是更专用的服务
Comment: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:50.29,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,然后在某一天对在托管平台之间切换感到有点恼火
Comment: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:54.11,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯   那会儿我们还得租服务器
Comment: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:59.13,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,你很难从那种小公司得到很好的远程支持
Comment: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:03.31,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,所以当 DigitalOcean 出现时   它非常诱人
Comment: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:06.47,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,它把这些都虚拟化
Comment: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:11.25,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,使得在不同服务器之间迁移变得容易得多
Comment: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:14.47,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,而且他们的支持也很不错
Comment: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:16.57,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,其服务水平是我以前从未经历过的好
Comment: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:19.91,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,osu! 的（服务器）数据库是 MySQL
Comment: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:22.01,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,十几年来   我们要拓展这些数据库
Comment: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:24.16,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,以前我们只有一个数据库
Comment: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:27.92,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但是现在它是一个小集群中运行的五个不同的服务
Comment: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:31.48,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,就这样不断拓展
Comment: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:34.19,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,真棒   下一个话题
Comment: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:40.57,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我们来谈谈一两年前我来见你的理由
Comment: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:45.20,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你正要迁移到 MongoDB 开发的 Realm 数据库
Comment: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:48.73,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,请聊聊这个过程   为什么你要迁移   你是怎么迁移的
Comment: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:52.67,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,这耗时多久   迁移的好处是什么
Comment: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:57.68,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,那么   这又是客户端方面的东西了
Comment: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:00.68,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们最初用的是 .NET Framework{\3c&H0000FF&}*
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:00.68,Explanation,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,*Stable 版本。
Comment: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:05.36,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,2017 年   我决定是时候重写游戏了
Comment: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:07.75,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,并且把这部分完全开源
Comment: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:11.23,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,尽可能保持透明一直是我的一个目标
Comment: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:13.93,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,那会儿   我想都没想就决定要开源
Comment: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:16.51,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,于是我切换到 .NET Core
Comment: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:20.49,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,在早期   我们用的是 SQLite
Comment: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:24.09,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,搭配 Entity Framework Core
Comment: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:29.79,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,有效是有效   但我们使用它的方式非常混乱
Comment: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:34.16,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,因为 Entity Framework 更多是为网站而打造的
Comment: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:36.83,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,其中所有内容都是一个线程模型
Comment: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:38.69,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,你接到一个请求
Comment: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:41.03,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,在该请求中执行各种操作
Comment: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:43.36,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这个请求就算完了
Comment: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:44.92,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,对游戏来讲却不是这样
Comment: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:47.51,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,它是要连着运行好几个小时的
Comment: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:51.13,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,所有这些线程在做不同的事情   却访问相同的数据
Comment: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:55.15,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,因此   虽然 EF 管用   但是它用起来非常混乱
Comment: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:58.25,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,当我们尝试从 EF2 迁移到 EF3 时
Comment: 0,0:21:58.51,0:22:02.48,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,在线程上有了新规则   于是我们遇到了所有这类问题
Comment: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:04.45,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这样   EF 就用不了了
Comment: 0,0:22:04.81,0:22:08.68,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们想修好线程模式
Comment: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:11.24,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,以及数据访问模式   Realm 就能做到
Comment: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:14.48,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,它非常诱人   它有资产合规性{\3c&H0000FF&}*
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:14.48,Explanation,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,,*Realm 文档和 GitHub Issue 都没有关于 "Assets Compliance" 的说法。本人没有 .NET 或 Realm 开发经验，欢迎大家提出更准确的译法。
Comment: 0,0:22:14.48,0:22:17.75,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,另外   Realm 对你怎样使用线程
Comment: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:21.75,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,非常严格   我认为这是一种好处
Comment: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:24.80,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,即使我们要投入一些初步努力来让它能用
Comment: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:26.71,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这意味着我们可以真正精简
Comment: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:30.95,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,简化我们的数据访问   迫使我们用更好的方式写代码
Comment: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:33.20,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,这很顽固   对吧
Comment: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.48,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,确实是
Comment: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:37.91,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,确实   但正如你所说   这是个好办法
Comment: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:38.64,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,是的
Comment: 0,0:22:39.36,0:22:42.37,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我想   你可能是在我们第一次谈话时开始迁移的
Comment: 0,0:22:42.37,0:22:47.00,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,当时正值 2020 年底   2021 年初
Comment: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:49.80,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,而且前一段时间已经完成了
Comment: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:55.25,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我想这不是一个你轻而易举就能完成的任务
Comment: 0,0:22:55.25,0:23:00.41,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,鉴于你要做的是整个游戏的重写
Comment: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:01.84,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,规模相当大
Comment: 0,0:23:02.47,0:23:05.56,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,osu! 的一个特点是   它是一个有大量数据的游戏
Comment: 0,0:23:05.56,0:23:07.68,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,因为大多数内容都是用户创造的
Comment: 0,0:23:07.68,0:23:13.12,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,客户端的本地数据库会相当大
Comment: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:16.39,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这就是我投入如此多心思的原因
Comment: 0,0:23:16.39,0:23:20.75,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,然后等待做出正确的决定   切换到 Realm
Comment: 0,0:23:21.15,0:23:24.75,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们从头开始尝试了三次
Comment: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:27.21,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们才让 Realm 能用起来
Comment: 0,0:23:27.60,0:23:31.03,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这费了好一番功夫   但最终证明一切顺利
Comment: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:33.60,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,挺幸运的
Comment: 0,0:23:34.75,0:23:36.45,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,非常高兴能听到这样的话
Comment: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:41.12,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,而且我知道   Realm 团队   尤其是 .NET SDK 团队
Comment: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:45.93,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,像 Nikolan 还有其他人   我们和他们进行了前后对话
Comment: 0,0:23:45.93,0:23:49.04,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,事实上   你发现的东西帮助了我们很多
Comment: 0,0:23:49.44,0:23:54.27,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,跟大多数开发者一样   通常   我们觉得
Comment: 0,0:23:54.27,0:23:57.77,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,在构建 Realm SDK 时   有时我们思考得过深了   过于尖刻了
Comment: 0,0:23:58.15,0:24:00.11,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,以至于无法弄清楚如何在实际场景中使用它
Comment: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:04.91,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,其他人使用 SDK 时   就会出现问题   用不了了
Comment: 0,0:24:04.91,0:24:10.32,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,所以我非常感谢你与我们的开发团队在这方面的互动   Dean
Comment: 0,0:24:10.57,0:24:14.40,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你帮了我们大忙
Comment: 0,0:24:14.81,0:24:19.67,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我想 Realm 开发团队听到它能够被实际应用时
Comment: 0,0:24:19.67,0:24:21.37,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,是很开心的
Comment: 0,0:24:21.61,0:24:24.03,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,这（对他们）大有裨益
Comment: 0,0:24:24.03,0:24:27.21,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,所以你最终对这一切都很满意
Comment: 0,0:24:27.97,0:24:30.84,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,确实   我们做到了
Comment: 0,0:24:30.84,0:24:35.84,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,现在新版游戏已经推向桌面平台   包括 Windows、Linux 和 macOS
Comment: 0,0:24:35.84,0:24:38.21,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,Realm 在所有这些平台上都表现出色
Comment: 0,0:24:38.21,0:24:43.01,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,游戏也有了 Android 和 iOS 版   尽管还在测试状态
Comment: 0,0:24:43.15,0:24:44.75,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们正计划把它推向更广的群体
Comment: 0,0:24:44.75,0:24:50.40,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,而 Realm 使得我们可以毫无问题地把它向所有这些平台上推出
Comment: 0,0:24:50.69,0:24:52.43,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这是我们的梦想
Comment: 0,0:24:52.53,0:24:56.44,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,虽然只要你把原生依赖配置好   SQLite 也能用
Comment: 0,0:24:56.44,0:24:58.35,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但你仍然要做好多工作
Comment: 0,0:24:58.67,0:25:01.87,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,而 Realm 把所有东西都准备好了   拿来就能用
Comment: 0,0:25:02.75,0:25:06.14,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,真是太好了   我要把这段播客剪下来
Comment: 0,0:25:06.14,0:25:08.58,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,发送给开发团队
Comment: 0,0:25:09.06,0:25:12.09,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,他们得到一手反馈会很高兴的
Comment: 0,0:25:12.59,0:25:17.15,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,之前你有说   osu! 的这次改变
Comment: 0,0:25:17.15,0:25:21.56,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,自你 2017 年开始重写起   你就把它开源了
Comment: 0,0:25:21.73,0:25:22.99,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,讲讲这里面的原因吧
Comment: 0,0:25:23.45,0:25:26.43,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,因为我一直很关心游戏的透明
Comment: 0,0:25:26.55,0:25:31.63,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,使开发过程透明   来尽可能地回报玩家社区
Comment: 0,0:25:31.63,0:25:35.47,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,也回报了开发社区
Comment: 0,0:25:35.57,0:25:40.07,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们社区中的很多玩家
Comment: 0,0:25:40.21,0:25:43.70,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我想   都相对年轻
Comment: 0,0:25:43.70,0:25:46.74,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,许多人在玩这款游戏的同时成长起来
Comment: 0,0:25:46.89,0:25:49.25,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,并自己加入了游戏开发
Comment: 0,0:25:49.58,0:25:54.31,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我认为   我们也有回馈这类玩家的可能
Comment: 0,0:25:54.31,0:25:58.71,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,让他们参与开发   而不仅仅是内容创作
Comment: 0,0:25:58.71,0:26:00.98,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,是要让人们直接对游戏开发做出贡献
Comment: 0,0:26:00.98,0:26:04.59,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这些年里   哪怕是我们还没开源的时候
Comment: 0,0:26:04.70,0:26:06.79,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,就有很多人问我   他们是否能够帮助游戏
Comment: 0,0:26:06.79,0:26:09.00,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们也提携了一些人
Comment: 0,0:26:09.00,0:26:12.58,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但始终存在着封闭代码的障碍
Comment: 0,0:26:12.87,0:26:15.13,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,（闭源时）向上游贡献东西并不容易
Comment: 0,0:26:15.57,0:26:19.99,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,是的   很明显   这确实是开源的主要好处
Comment: 0,0:26:19.99,0:26:22.85,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,MongoDB 也是源于开源的
Comment: 0,0:26:23.25,0:26:25.55,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你是怎么管理这些贡献
Comment: 0,0:26:25.73,0:26:29.59,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,处理各种提拉取请求的呢
Comment: 0,0:26:29.59,0:26:34.93,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我去看了你们的网站   新版客户端看起来周更一次
Comment: 0,0:26:35.28,0:26:38.89,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,更新日志一大堆   许多人都在帮忙
Comment: 0,0:26:38.89,0:26:43.89,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,Dean   你的小团队是怎么管理的
Comment: 0,0:26:43.89,0:26:48.13,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,从开发者角度讲   也是有很多压力的
Comment: 0,0:26:48.55,0:26:53.21,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们收到的低质量拉取请求和问题报告太多太多
Comment: 0,0:26:53.31,0:26:57.21,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这还是在我们开始适应这个开源版本之前就有的现象
Comment: 0,0:26:57.21,0:26:59.32,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,新版仍然处于测试状态
Comment: 0,0:26:59.77,0:27:02.91,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,到现在为止   我们还没有将其推广到全用户群
Comment: 0,0:27:02.91,0:27:06.62,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,因为我们知道   一旦更多用户加入
Comment: 0,0:27:06.62,0:27:08.89,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们只会被更多的支持请求淹没
Comment: 0,0:27:09.31,0:27:12.53,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,所以   尽管有成千上万人
Comment: 0,0:27:12.71,0:27:15.83,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,已经用过新版本
Comment: 0,0:27:16.01,0:27:19.98,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但实际的游戏群体比这要高好几个数量级
Comment: 0,0:27:20.57,0:27:23.87,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,对于我们如何管理它   我真的没有什么经验
Comment: 0,0:27:23.89,0:27:28.73,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,此外   如何真正跟上开源贡献和讨论
Comment: 0,0:27:28.88,0:27:30.55,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,以及随之而来的其他一切
Comment: 0,0:27:30.68,0:27:35.63,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,仍然是一个持续的关注点和冲突点
Comment: 0,0:27:35.94,0:27:38.45,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我想   这是你和社区一起走开源道路时
Comment: 0,0:27:38.45,0:27:41.18,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,难免碰到的一件事情
Comment: 0,0:27:41.63,0:27:43.37,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,必然会招致一些抱怨
Comment: 0,0:27:43.37,0:27:46.65,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你有一大堆拉取请求   有一堆人反馈问题
Comment: 0,0:27:46.65,0:27:48.79,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,也有不少人帮你修复问题
Comment: 0,0:27:49.04,0:27:51.16,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,那是站在管理层的角度来看是这样的
Comment: 0,0:27:51.23,0:27:55.24,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,但在我的角度   在我的眼里   你做的事可太精彩了
Comment: 0,0:27:55.24,0:27:57.55,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你让这个项目活跃了起来
Comment: 0,0:27:57.55,0:28:03.53,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,要管理那种水平的提升   需要大量的工作
Comment: 0,0:28:03.53,0:28:06.53,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,非常棒   这是新版客户端   对吧
Comment: 0,0:28:07.27,0:28:08.11,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,是的
Comment: 0,0:28:08.65,0:28:11.27,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,它已经酝酿一段时间了
Comment: 0,0:28:11.27,0:28:16.20,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你什么时候把它完全推向更广的社区
Comment: 0,0:28:16.20,0:28:19.25,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯   我们从 2017 年开始开发
Comment: 0,0:28:19.25,0:28:23.91,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,到现在终于要接近完成了
Comment: 0,0:28:23.91,0:28:27.45,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们会在今年或明年全面推出它
Comment: 0,0:28:27.87,0:28:29.21,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,一切都已基本就绪
Comment: 0,0:28:29.21,0:28:31.88,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,现在更多的是关乎用户体验
Comment: 0,0:28:32.11,0:28:33.94,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,要确保大家期待的特性
Comment: 0,0:28:34.15,0:28:38.32,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,因为我们这些年在游戏中新增了大量特性
Comment: 0,0:28:38.32,0:28:41.64,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,玩家多年期望的特性应该在 Lazer 上出现
Comment: 0,0:28:42.19,0:28:46.40,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,并且   我最初开发游戏的方式是
Comment: 0,0:28:46.40,0:28:50.36,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,仅仅是把最多的精力投入在功能上
Comment: 0,0:28:50.36,0:28:52.35,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,不怎么关心代码质量
Comment: 0,0:28:52.35,0:28:53.88,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,现在   我们恰好反过来
Comment: 0,0:28:53.88,0:28:57.23,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们要确保在未来   游戏是可维护的
Comment: 0,0:28:57.34,0:29:01.50,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,哪怕是我停止开发了   或者我消失了   其他人需要接管
Comment: 0,0:29:01.98,0:29:06.11,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我尽量完整地把一切写在文档里
Comment: 0,0:29:06.11,0:29:09.20,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,要让别人能非常兴奋地接管这个项目
Comment: 0,0:29:09.20,0:29:13.08,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,而不是看着这个代码库   然后想   “卧槽   我得到的是啥玩意”
Comment: 0,0:29:14.40,0:29:18.07,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,目前是否有什么东西阻碍了 osu! 的成长
Comment: 0,0:29:18.07,0:29:21.52,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,或者卡住了 osu! 的规模   还是说你对目前的一切都满意
Comment: 0,0:29:21.52,0:29:25.62,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,或者说有没有什么让你一直沮丧的事
Comment: 0,0:29:25.62,0:29:29.09,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,是技术困难   还是社区交流受挫呢
Comment: 0,0:29:29.42,0:29:32.12,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我倒不这么想   我们主要考虑的是
Comment: 0,0:29:32.12,0:29:34.11,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,把新版本做好   推向用户
Comment: 0,0:29:34.20,0:29:37.42,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,弄清楚需要做什么
Comment: 0,0:29:37.51,0:29:41.22,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,还剩什么要做   来使大多数玩家满意
Comment: 0,0:29:41.76,0:29:46.76,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我认为最难的事是管理团队
Comment: 0,0:29:46.76,0:29:50.48,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,管理我们从这一代玩家那里得到的反馈
Comment: 0,0:29:50.48,0:29:54.77,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,在这个时代   少数派的意见尤其大
Comment: 0,0:29:54.77,0:29:56.86,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,经常对缺失的东西或做错的事情直言不讳
Comment: 0,0:29:57.10,0:29:59.82,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,从社区的大部分人的角度来看
Comment: 0,0:29:59.82,0:30:01.57,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,大多数人对现状很满意
Comment: 0,0:30:02.35,0:30:06.68,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们还要支持人们使用的不同硬件
Comment: 0,0:30:06.68,0:30:08.94,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,无论什么设备   都要发挥良好性能
Comment: 0,0:30:08.94,0:30:12.06,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,玩家可能会在 10 年甚至 15 年前的电脑上
Comment: 0,0:30:12.70,0:30:15.63,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,在那里玩 osu!   他们期望 osu! 能很好地运行
Comment: 0,0:30:15.63,0:30:18.82,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,你知道   用最新的类库和组件重新开发
Comment: 0,0:30:18.82,0:30:21.37,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,又要保证向后兼容性   是个很大的挑战
Comment: 0,0:30:21.43,0:30:23.77,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,跨平台的东西很难管理
Comment: 0,0:30:23.77,0:30:26.96,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,正如你所说   客户端有 Windows、Linux 和 macOS 版本
Comment: 0,0:30:27.39,0:30:30.90,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,还有 iOS 和 Android 的测试版   是吧
Comment: 0,0:30:31.42,0:30:34.49,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,但是还处于初步测试阶段
Comment: 0,0:30:34.79,0:30:36.78,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,如你所言
Comment: 0,0:30:36.78,0:30:40.08,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,有句谚语叫   会哭的孩子吃奶多
Comment: 0,0:30:40.08,0:30:43.21,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我觉得这就是你要和社区尽力去跳开的怪圈
Comment: 0,0:30:43.21,0:30:46.62,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,总有些人直言不讳   大声批评
Comment: 0,0:30:46.62,0:30:49.53,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,但他们只是极少数人
Comment: 0,0:30:49.53,0:30:53.90,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,然而   对这感到满意的玩家
Comment: 0,0:30:53.97,0:30:57.00,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,Lazer 成千上万的用户可以证明这点
Comment: 0,0:30:57.00,0:31:01.57,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,那些非常快乐和满足的玩家占大多数
Comment: 0,0:31:01.57,0:31:06.02,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,但你不一定会从这些人那里得到反馈
Comment: 0,0:31:06.02,0:31:07.48,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,他们只是乐意玩下去   默默支持
Comment: 0,0:31:07.69,0:31:09.77,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但另一件要记住的事是
Comment: 0,0:31:09.77,0:31:12.84,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,（少数人的）这些反馈通常出于好意
Comment: 0,0:31:12.84,0:31:15.24,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,他们直言不讳   是因为他们关心游戏
Comment: 0,0:31:15.24,0:31:19.52,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,对他们自己和别人预期的游戏表现非常上心
Comment: 0,0:31:19.52,0:31:23.75,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,因此   我们肯定会尽力听取每一个反馈意见
Comment: 0,0:31:23.75,0:31:28.07,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我也尽力回复每一封邮件
Comment: 0,0:31:28.07,0:31:32.67,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,对我来说   保持与社区的联系是一个相当大的时间耗费
Comment: 0,0:31:32.67,0:31:36.68,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但我觉得这很重要   即使是它占用了一点开发时间
Comment: 0,0:31:36.86,0:31:41.45,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我想   Lazer 最重要的下一步显然是
Comment: 0,0:31:41.74,0:31:43.47,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,把它推向其余的玩家群群
Comment: 0,0:31:44.23,0:31:46.85,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,在这之后还有计划吗   Dean
Comment: 0,0:31:46.85,0:31:50.66,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,比如   把它推出去后   我们还有甲乙丙三步走
Comment: 0,0:31:50.66,0:31:52.71,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你可以告诉我们吗
Comment: 0,0:31:52.71,0:31:55.16,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,亦或是你脱出身来   给自己放个长假
Comment: 0,0:31:55.63,0:31:59.88,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯   我特别想做的事之一就是
Comment: 0,0:31:59.88,0:32:02.69,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,在别的项目上工作
Comment: 0,0:32:02.69,0:32:06.53,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,尝试些新东西   甚至为别人工作都有可能
Comment: 0,0:32:06.53,0:32:07.82,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,这样从 osu! 的位子上退下来
Comment: 0,0:32:07.82,0:32:09.19,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但我不认为这种事会发生
Comment: 0,0:32:09.40,0:32:12.50,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我们太慢了   我们有大量积压的功能还没完成
Comment: 0,0:32:12.85,0:32:16.02,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,目前   我们正在尝试用旧版本进行功能模仿
Comment: 0,0:32:16.02,0:32:19.84,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但在那之后   又有太多用户的请求   看不到尽头
Comment: 0,0:32:20.03,0:32:21.25,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,有点吓人
Comment: 0,0:32:21.50,0:32:23.35,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,看不到尽头   确实吓人
Comment: 0,0:32:23.35,0:32:26.05,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,但这是一个巨大挑战
Comment: 0,0:32:26.49,0:32:29.15,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,而且到目前为止   你显然已经为此付出了十五年的时间
Comment: 0,0:32:29.41,0:32:29.73,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,是的
Comment: 0,0:32:30.03,0:32:35.75,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,而且鉴于你已经把兴趣爱好变成了日常业务
Comment: 0,0:32:35.75,0:32:40.18,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,还雇了别人去做这事   建立起巨大的全球社区
Comment: 0,0:32:40.25,0:32:42.67,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我觉得大家都不想你退下来   Dean
Comment: 0,0:32:42.67,0:32:46.15,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,显然他们盼望着建起越来越多的东西
Comment: 0,0:32:46.30,0:32:47.49,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,拓展 osu! 的规模
Comment: 0,0:32:47.88,0:32:50.89,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,确实   我也不想别人做我做的事情
Comment: 0,0:32:50.89,0:32:55.29,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,可能我是有些变态
Comment: 0,0:32:55.29,0:32:57.24,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,才能一直坐着这个位子吧
Comment: 0,0:32:57.49,0:33:00.51,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但同时   还有另一点要说明
Comment: 0,0:33:01.23,0:33:04.44,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,就是无论未来会发生什么   我都乐于接受
Comment: 0,0:33:04.44,0:33:07.24,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我对我们今天所取得的一切非常满意
Comment: 0,0:33:07.24,0:33:10.28,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我认为重要的是   把这些事情一天天做下去
Comment: 0,0:33:10.28,0:33:15.22,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,十五年来   这么多人享受我们的游戏
Comment: 0,0:33:15.56,0:33:18.63,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,因此就算我们今天就毁掉一切
Comment: 0,0:33:18.63,0:33:21.13,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我都（不遗憾）   还算满意
Comment: 0,0:33:21.13,0:33:24.25,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,因为我们在过去十多年间给予了人们许多快乐
Comment: 0,0:33:24.25,0:33:27.95,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,是的   我必须对你的这一做法表示赞赏
Comment: 0,0:33:28.13,0:33:29.72,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,对你说的这些我都很认可
Comment: 0,0:33:29.72,0:33:35.86,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,显然   这种享受本身就是对你创造 osu! 的奖励
Comment: 0,0:33:36.21,0:33:38.87,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,无论如何   在我看来
Comment: 0,0:33:38.87,0:33:43.98,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你没有试图特意地超越其手段来发展它
Comment: 0,0:33:43.98,0:33:47.56,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,或者公然将其货币化   设置游玩障碍
Comment: 0,0:33:47.93,0:33:52.31,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,通过支持者标签系统
Comment: 0,0:33:52.31,0:33:56.52,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你传递了一个信号   我们确实需要收钱来维持 osu! 的发展
Comment: 0,0:33:56.52,0:33:59.18,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,但我们自有分寸   取财有道
Comment: 0,0:33:59.18,0:34:01.98,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我认为这有一些令人难以置信的利他主义
Comment: 0,0:34:01.98,0:34:04.69,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,比如你的开源举动   比如你管理它的方式
Comment: 0,0:34:04.69,0:34:08.37,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,所以我认为你已经做出了惊人的努力
Comment: 0,0:34:08.37,0:34:12.96,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我非常期待 osu! 的持续发展
Comment: 0,0:34:12.96,0:34:16.89,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,您还有什么想与播客观众分享的吗
Comment: 0,0:34:16.89,0:34:19.72,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,正如我前面提到的
Comment: 0,0:34:19.72,0:34:24.16,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,有许多开发者希望把他们的爱好
Comment: 0,0:34:24.16,0:34:26.55,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,他们的兴趣   变成他们的职业
Comment: 0,0:34:26.93,0:34:30.74,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,而你显然已经做到了这一点   你有了这样的经验并分享出来
Comment: 0,0:34:31.15,0:34:34.75,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,对那些可能在这一边缘徘徊的开发者有什么建议吗
Comment: 0,0:34:34.75,0:34:38.68,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,尤其是在疫情下   人们在家里工作
Comment: 0,0:34:38.68,0:34:42.95,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,他们现在意识到   不需要一个办公室就能上班
Comment: 0,0:34:42.95,0:34:46.52,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你不需要在特定的时间段内出现在特定的地方
Comment: 0,0:34:46.56,0:34:50.94,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,因此我认为   机会正在向开发者招手
Comment: 0,0:34:51.24,0:34:54.47,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,吸引他们承担自己的项目和副业
Comment: 0,0:34:54.47,0:34:55.83,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,他们可能会寻求和运行这些项目
Comment: 0,0:34:55.83,0:35:00.65,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,是的   我一直认为
Comment: 0,0:35:00.65,0:35:03.25,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我所有的副业   所做的一切
Comment: 0,0:35:03.25,0:35:07.09,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,都是我既感兴趣的东西   也是我自己想要为之努力的东西
Comment: 0,0:35:07.09,0:35:09.63,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,无论是不是改善现有的服务
Comment: 0,0:35:09.88,0:35:11.57,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,那种不能完全做我想做的事的服务
Comment: 0,0:35:11.73,0:35:14.68,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我都是为我自己开发   然后把它公开
Comment: 0,0:35:14.68,0:35:16.90,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,如果它流行起来   那么它确实成功
Comment: 0,0:35:16.90,0:35:21.09,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,但我在开发时   并不考虑营销
Comment: 0,0:35:21.09,0:35:23.92,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,也不会真的考虑在财务上是否可行
Comment: 0,0:35:23.92,0:35:28.09,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,我认为最重要的是现在就开始   纯粹地试着制造一个令人惊叹的产品
Comment: 0,0:35:28.33,0:35:32.10,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,在过去   这种例子数不胜数
Comment: 0,0:35:32.10,0:35:36.52,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,特别是科技领域的开发者想要满足自己的需求   想解决的问题
Comment: 0,0:35:36.52,0:35:40.28,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,突然间   这个项目滚雪球一样迅速扩大   变成另一种东西
Comment: 0,0:35:40.28,0:35:42.60,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,但是   在你身上
Comment: 0,0:35:42.60,0:35:47.60,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我对你在 osu! 上建立的东西和你建立的方式印象深刻
Comment: 0,0:35:47.60,0:35:49.53,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,这次谈话真是引人入胜
Comment: 0,0:35:49.53,0:35:53.97,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,结束之前   我想再问一遍
Comment: 0,0:35:53.97,0:35:56.37,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,到哪里可以玩到 osu!
Comment: 0,0:35:56.63,0:36:01.67,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,它的 GitHub 仓库在哪里   这样大家就可以成为社区一员并贡献了
Comment: 0,0:36:01.87,0:36:06.19,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,那么   你可以进入 osu.ppy.sh 下载游戏
Comment: 0,0:36:06.33,0:36:10.12,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,或者去 GitHub   我们的账号是 @ppy   所有东西都在那里
Comment: 0,0:36:10.20,0:36:11.79,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,好的   这次谈话真棒
Comment: 0,0:36:11.79,0:36:14.09,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,非常感谢你抽出时间来参加我们的会议
Comment: 0,0:36:14.17,0:36:17.84,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,正如你之前提到的   你并不把它视为工作
Comment: 0,0:36:17.92,0:36:20.90,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我可以证明这一点   因为你在日本   我在爱尔兰
Comment: 0,0:36:20.90,0:36:24.50,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我们之间有九个小时的时差   而且你那边已经很迟了
Comment: 0,0:36:24.88,0:36:26.99,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你很乐意加入这次播客
Comment: 0,0:36:27.27,0:36:29.02,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,因此   谢谢你   Dean
Comment: 0,0:36:29.02,0:36:31.40,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,很高兴你能加入我们
Comment: 0,0:36:31.40,0:36:35.04,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我们期待着关注 osu! 的进展
Comment: 0,0:36:35.54,0:36:37.52,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,karaoke,好的   谢谢   Shane   这次对话真棒
Comment: 0,0:36:38.54,0:36:42.33,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,你很可能看出来了   我很享受与 Dean 的对话
Comment: 0,0:36:42.65,0:36:47.55,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,他对 osu! 和对 osu! 社区的奉献程度让我惊讶
Comment: 0,0:36:48.06,0:36:52.02,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,对他来说   这不仅仅是一份工作或一份业务
Comment: 0,0:36:52.45,0:36:56.71,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,这一切背后都有一种目标感   社区感和远见
Comment: 0,0:36:57.34,0:37:00.94,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我非常期待看到 osu! 继续成功
Comment: 0,0:37:01.24,0:37:02.85,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,如果你想试玩 osu!
Comment: 0,0:37:03.20,0:37:07.50,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,请打开我们提到的网址
Comment: 0,0:37:07.84,0:37:09.46,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,请一定要来看看它
Comment: 0,0:37:10.34,0:37:13.13,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,另外   如果你像 Dean 一样   也有着吸引我们听众的故事
Comment: 0,0:37:13.38,0:37:16.62,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我们一直在寻找 MongoDB 播客的嘉宾
Comment: 0,0:37:16.93,0:37:18.95,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,所以如果你觉得你可以做贡献
Comment: 0,0:37:19.30,0:37:23.31,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,请联系我们   地址是 podcast@mongodb.com
Comment: 0,0:37:23.63,0:37:25.25,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,我们非常希望听到您的故事
Comment: 0,0:37:26.47,0:37:29.34,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,感谢倾听   我们不胜感激
Comment: 0,0:37:29.56,0:37:31.92,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,如果你喜欢这集
Comment: 0,0:37:31.92,0:37:37.50,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,无论你用哪个播客软件   请打个分或留下评论
Comment: 0,0:37:37.78,0:37:39.02,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,这对我们帮助很大
Comment: 0,0:37:39.56,0:37:42.83,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,请务必关注我   Shane McAllister   以及播客团队的其他成员
Comment: 0,0:37:43.46,0:37:46.82,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,karaoke,谢谢收听   我们下次再见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.24,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}你好   我是 Dean   这里是 MongoDB 播客
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:05.72,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}今天我们来聊聊我创造的一款叫 osu! 的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:09.15,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}欢迎来到 MongoDB 播客
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:12.15,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}和往常一样   感谢您加入我们新的一集专访
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.43,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我的名字叫 Shane McAllister
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:17.56,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}如果现在不算太迟的话   祝各位新年快乐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:21.12,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}另外   我们非常期待今年的超级碗比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:24.12,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}而且我们还会带来一些激动人心的专访
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:27.68,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}还是那句话   无论你用的是哪个播客软件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:29.99,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}都请点击“订阅”按钮   关注我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:31.76,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}这样你就不会错过我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:35.83,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}在这一周的专访中   我们要深入游戏领域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:39.09,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}尤其是节奏游戏*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:43.01,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}今天很高兴邀请到 Dean Herbert   osu! 的创造者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:46.50,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}osu! 是个倍受欢迎的在线节奏游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:51.44,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}它是开源软件*   用到了 MongoDB 的 Realm .NET SDK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:56.80,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}本期访谈中   我们要了解它的开端   为什么 Dean 创造了它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:01.94,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}自从 Dean 单枪匹马地创造它以来   它是怎样在多年间取得巨大发展的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.13,0:01:05.55,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}以及他是怎么把这项爱好变成全职职业的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.70,0:01:08.83,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}他是怎么建立起一个庞大而忠诚的追随者社区的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:10.32,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}让我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:14.24,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}今天   在这里   我们邀请到了 Dean
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:18.32,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}Dean   请你对 MongoDB 播客的观众做个自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:20.37,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}告诉我们你是谁   你干的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:23.87,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}嗨   我是 Dean   我创造了一个叫 osu! 的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:29.81,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}自 2007 年来我就一直致力于此   所以在过去十五年间它成了我的一种生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:32.67,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我从一个爱好做起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.67,0:01:38.43,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我就无法自拔   因为我总是对节奏游戏和诸如此类的事情感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:41.47,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我在澳大利亚长大   度过童年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:46.24,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}那会儿我们还有开这种节奏游戏的机厅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:50.99,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我一直喜欢音乐和游戏   所以这种组合真的打动了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:53.41,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}但是那种机厅并不多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:58.09,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}而且没过多久它们就会关闭   所有这些游戏都会突然消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:00.05,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}于是   当互联网出现时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:03.53,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}有的人就做了这类节奏游戏的在线模拟器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:08.03,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}突然间   我就又能在电脑上玩到它们   想玩啥就玩啥了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:10.39,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}这就是 osu! 诞生的背景
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:12.68,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}那我们就回到开头的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:16.43,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}osu! 是有个日语含义对吧   另外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:19.44,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我们的听众是相当广泛和多样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:22.39,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}有的听众可能并不了解什么是“节奏游戏”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:25.53,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}你能解释一下这些游戏的起源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:27.29,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}玩这些会涉及什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:28.25,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.75,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}节奏游戏有很多风格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.32,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}而 osu! 是基于
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:36.43,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}是基于一款发布在 NDS 上的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:39.43,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}叫做《押忍！战斗！应援团》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:42.67,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}这是一款故事驱动的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.93,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}游戏中   你会和啦啦队队员一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.81,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}这些队员都是男的   叫做“应援团”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:52.88,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}而“osu!”(押忍！)是他们的一个口号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:55.88,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}他们想鼓励那些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:59.59,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}那些经历过人生低谷的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:02.88,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}你得随着音乐玩这款游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:06.83,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}在 NDS 屏幕上点击   让他们情绪高涨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.11,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}最后拨云见日   屡战屡胜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:10.65,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}这就是 osu! 的起源   我玩了那款游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:14.48,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}但显然   因为它是面向一个小游戏机系统发布的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:17.51,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}你只能玩到游戏自带的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:21.08,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我就马上想要往里面加自己选的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.25,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}相当于创建新关卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:24.88,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}于是 osu! 就诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:29.79,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}那么   自从你开始   已经十五年了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:33.00,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}现在它规模有多大   它的团队有多大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:35.52,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}以及你在团队中的日常角色是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:40.36,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}在头五年   好像还多几年   是只有我在维护这个游戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:43.69,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}开始是作为一个爱好   最后就（辞职开发游戏了）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:47.04,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我原来是全职 .NET 程序员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:50.83,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}当时我做的是把 J2EE 系统迁移到 .NET
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:55.00,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}所以我有丰富的 .NET 开发经验
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.36,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}是的   最初只由我业余搞搞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.80,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}这些年来   人们对这个游戏越来越感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:06.15,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}然后他们真的投入金钱贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:08.68,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}于是我就全职开发游戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:11.56,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}很了不起   因为在我的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:15.13,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我遇到过许多失意的游戏开发者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:17.57,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}他们也走在（游戏开发之）路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:21.05,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}就和你的描述一样    追寻他们的激情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:22.83,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}追随他们感兴趣的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:26.37,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}然而   把它作为全职工作真的很不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.20,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}但你做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:30.44,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}嗯   或许我有运气成分在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:33.95,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我就是对这游戏有极大的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:37.00,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}于是我醒着的每一刻都投入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:42.41,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}很多时候   我每天只睡三个小时   这样一干就是好几年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:47.07,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}当我年轻的时候   我一直在做这个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:50.16,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}大家看到了   因为我的投入   这个游戏变化之大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:52.12,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}（大家也看到）我倾听用户反馈的次数之多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:54.39,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}然后我就满足他们要求的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:58.11,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}早年间   我取得了一些非常快速的开发进展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:00.57,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}也许代价就是代码质量很差
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:04.19,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}但是   这些年里   我们扩大了团队规模
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:07.19,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}现在一共有八人在全职开发 osu! 了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:11.04,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}包括游戏的各种元素   客户端及其背后的基础设施
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:15.93,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}而且我们还有大量的社区贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:18.93,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}基本上   是志愿者在保持内容的产出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:22.97,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}游戏的策划系统   运行在线社区的管理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:26.17,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}你居住在日本   团队中的其他人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:29.49,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}他们也在日本么   还是说你们遍布世界各处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:32.36,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}是的   我们确实有几个开发者在日本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.71,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}但大多数成员是远程工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.01,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}其实我们一直
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:40.71,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}基本上把人们从志愿者角色提升到全职角色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:43.53,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}他们一直在他们那里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:46.27,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}所以有几个在美国   有几个在澳大利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:49.27,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}还有些在东亚   反正是遍布全球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:52.52,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}那很精彩诶   那么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:57.32,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}你提到最初这个游戏是基于一款 NDS 游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:00.60,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}显然   世界上还有其他类型的节奏游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.47,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}是什么使 osu! 与所有这些都与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:07.12,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我想主要是因为我们的动力大部分来自社区
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:09.79,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我们致力于用户内容   所以 osu! 从第一天起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:12.72,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}就自带一个编辑器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.39,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}你可以在那里创建游戏关卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.25,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}osu! 从来不自带关卡*
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:20.95,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}要制作什么完全取决于用户
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:23.95,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}还有一件事情是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:26.51,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我们一直在尝试着以一种
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:29.11,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}与游戏工业有天差地别的方式来运营游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:33.55,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我并不喜欢当今把游戏给货币化的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:37.81,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}所以我总是以玩家想要的方式去运营
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:40.23,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}从未想过在游戏中获利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.37,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}于是你就从那样的角度对待了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:47.55,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}所以这当然会让我们想到收入的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:50.45,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我浏览了 osu! 网站
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.93,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}你们有家很棒的装饰品商店   尤其是那个抱枕*   我挺喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.04,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}很明显   那里有很多收入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:07:00.93,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}但是 osu! 是怎么坚持的呢   你们八个人靠什么吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:03.44,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}是的   所以我们确实有商品方面的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.27,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}但那点钱算是（杯水车薪）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:08.81,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}那点收入只能涵盖比赛奖金之类的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:12.64,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}现在   我们的大多数收入来自玩家的直接捐赠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:15.57,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我们有一套系统叫“支持者标签”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:21.40,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}玩家买个几月几年的支持者标签
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.07,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我们就给予他们一些游戏内的额外功能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:26.11,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}比如   自定义个人主页
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:30.56,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}还有一些游戏内部的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:32.77,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}更便利的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:37.25,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}与一般玩家相比能支配的东西更多   就像这样的几个功能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:40.00,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我一直把这些特权放在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:42.36,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}花费我们更多精力的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:44.36,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}于是这之间有了实在的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.01,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}即   你出钱   就有相应回报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.72,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}挺有趣的   另外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:53.21,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我想我们已经习惯了更大的游戏领域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:57.35,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}但那些游戏的赚钱心可能更强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:08:02.29,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}它的利润很大   但游戏规模也会越大   开发团队也越大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:06.99,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}成本等等也越大   接着我们来谈谈游戏社区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:10.05,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}你运营的社区实在让人印象深刻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:13.09,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}但是我们还得补充下背景   比如你刚才提到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:17.51,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}你创立 osu! 时   并没有现成的谱面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.72,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}你只能自己做   这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:21.93,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}什么是“谱面”   谱面是怎么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:25.57,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}这十多年来   玩家们一共做了多少谱面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:27.40,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}啊   那是另外一回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:31.76,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我第一次完成这个游戏时   电脑平台上已经有些这个游戏的模拟器了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:37.13,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}但它们都没有能让你能够直接创作关卡的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:42.52,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}而   自 osu! 的主菜单中   你就可以进入编辑器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:45.52,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}拖进一个你想做关卡的 MP3
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:51.65,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}对好节奏   敲鼓点来把 BPM 设置好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:55.23,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}而后你就可以在屏幕上开始布置物件了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:57.49,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我们有三种物件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:09:01.55,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}一是圆圈   二是滑条   会持续一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:04.04,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}三是转盘   一种小把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.75,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}你要以最快的速度转动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.68,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}所以它给了你很大的灵活性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.91,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}每首歌你都能随心所欲地制作关卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:14.16,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:17.85,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}你在放置物件时   可以赋予它们特殊的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:23.16,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}所以你实际上可以在原始歌曲上创建一个鼓点节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.57,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}给予它新的特征
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:29.63,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}这就是我对这个游戏感兴趣的原因之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:32.09,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}比起其他节奏游戏来说    任天堂的这款
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:35.84,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}应该是 INIS   他们才是原开发者   他们在原曲之上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:38.31,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}创造了新的声音景观
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.23,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}他们存留在我的脑海中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:43.64,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}每次我在电台里听到一首歌   我就能听到这些节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.15,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我就想在原曲上加入这些节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:50.31,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}所以如果你要上传一个 MP3    是任意的 MP3 都能用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:54.16,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}还是说   这本身就存在版权问题   我能想象得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:58.16,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}你把 MP3 拖进来时    一切操作都在本地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.92,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}所以   理论上讲   你可以做任何事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.64,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}那就是说   你也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:07.04,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}用热门曲目来制谱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.93,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}但它存储在本地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:12.19,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}但是我们是允许把它们上传到服务器的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:15.69,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}所以   很长一段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:17.33,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}这都是用户创作的天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:19.80,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}当然   如果收到（下架）请求   我们肯定会下架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.51,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}但有件好事是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:27.12,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}最近这五六年   我们有了可观的盈利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:30.97,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我们把这些收入都投入到音乐版权中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:32.72,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我们已经追溯到了过去那些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:36.59,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}谱面库里最受欢迎的谱面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:41.16,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我们会联系那些艺术家   现在我们已经买下了约四千首歌的版权
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.93,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}好像是所有节奏游戏中最多的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:48.27,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我们已经尽力把它们带回来   能合法地使用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:51.47,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我喜欢这个故事   挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:54.39,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}那么    osu! 谱面库到现在一共有多少谱面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:58.72,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}嗯   超过两百万
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:02.11,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}此外   我们还有一套机制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:04.63,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}来保证谱面的质量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:07.64,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}叫做“上架状态”*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:09.16,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}上架的谱面会开放排行榜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:10.89,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}还会有一些特殊特性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:13.52,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}目前上架谱面大约有五万个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.81,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}哇   所以说   在这个规模的谱面库上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.07,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}osu! 社区又有多大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:21.39,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}玩家共有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:24.05,Chinese,Shane McAllister,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}他们在哪些国家   他们多长时间玩一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.09,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}好的   那么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:29.08,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}我们的注册用户大约有三千万
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:31.72,Chinese,Dean Herbert,0,0,0,fx,{\pos(960,1027)}在高峰期   同时在线人数
